var book = {
	"name": "Lewitikɔs",
	"numChapters": 27,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE frɛɛ Mose, na ɔfiri ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu kasa kyerɛɛ no sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ, na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ mo mu nipa bi de ayɛyɛdeɛ rebrɛ AWURADE a, afieboa a ɔfiri anantwie ne nnwan mu na momfa nyɛ mo ayɛyɛdeɛ mmra.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no yɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a ɛfiri anantwie mu a, ɔmfa onini a ɔdi mu mmra; ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano na ɔmfa no mmra, na wasɔ AWURADE ani.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔmfa ne nsa nto ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no atifi, na ɛnsɔ ani mma no na ɛmpata mma no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔnkum nantwinini no, AWURADE anim, na Aaron mma asɔfoɔ no, mfa mogya no mmra, na wɔmfa mpete afɔrebukyia a ɛwɔ ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no so nhyia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔnnwa ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no nwoma, na ɔntwitwa no asinasini.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Ɔsɔfoɔ Aaron mma no nsiesie nnyina wɔ afɔrebukyia no so, na wɔnsɔ ano.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Aaron mma asɔfoɔ no, mfa asinasini no, botire no ne sradeɛ no ngu nnyina a ɛwɔ afɔrebukyia no gya no so.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔnhohoro n’ayamdeɛ ne ne nnyawa ho wɔ nsuo mu; na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye ne nyinaa afɔrebukyia no so, na ɛnyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no firi nnwan mu, nnwanten anaa mmirekyie mu, na ɔde rekɔbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a, onini a ɔdi mu na ɔmfa mmra.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔnku no afɔrebukyia no nkyɛn mu atifi fam, AWURADE anim, na Aaron mma asɔfoɔ no, mfa ne mogya mpete afɔrebukyia no so nhyia.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔntwitwa mu, n’asinasini no mu, ɛne ne ti ne ne sradeɛ nyinaa na ɔsɔfoɔ no nsiesie ngu afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ayamdeɛ ne nnyawa no, ɔmfa nsuo nhohoro ho; na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nyinaa mmra mmɛhye no afɔrebukyia no so; ɛyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no firi ntakraboa mu na ɔde rebɛbɔ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE a, ɔmfa anyankuku anaa mmorɔnoma mma nyɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ mmra.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa mmra afɔrebukyia no ho, na ɔnte ne ti na ɔnhye no afɔrebukyia no so, na ɔnkyi ne mogya ngu afɔrebukyia no ho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔnyi ne mene ase ne deɛ ɛwɔ mu nto ntwene afɔrebukyia no nkyɛn apueeɛ fam, deɛ nso guo hɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔnsuane no mu, n’atabu so, nanso ɔnnte mu, na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye wɔ afɔrebukyia no so; ɛyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na sɛ obi de aduane afɔdeɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ rebrɛ AWURADE a, n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no nyɛ esiam, na ɔngu so ngo, na ɔmfa ohwamfufuo nto so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔmfa mmrɛ Aaron mma no, asɔfoɔ no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa esiam ne ngo no nsa mama, ne ohwamfufuo no nyinaa, na ɔnhye wɔ afɔrebukyia no so sɛ nkaeɛ adeɛ. Ɛyɛ ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na aduane afɔdeɛ no mu deɛ ɛbɛka no nyɛ Aaron ne ne mma dea, AWURADE gya mu akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron ne no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na sɛ wode aduane afɔdeɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ a wɔato no fononoo mu bi reba a, fa esiam apiti a wɔde ngo afɔre taterɛ ne apiti ɔfam a wɔagu so ngo bra.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ w’ayɛyɛdeɛ no yɛ aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔakye no dadeɛ so a, ma no nyɛ esiam apiti a wɔde ngo afɔre;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bubu mu asinasini, na hwie ngo gu so, aduane afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ w’ayɛyɛdeɛ no yɛ kukuo mu aduane afɔdeɛ a, fa esiam ne ngo yɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na fa aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔde nnoɔma yi ayɛ no brɛ AWURADE; na wɔde brɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no a, ɔmfa mmra afɔrebukyia no ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nyi ayɛyɛdeɛ no so nkaeɛ adeɛ no, na ɔnhye wɔ afɔrebukyia no so; ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE ne no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na aduane afɔdeɛ no nkaeɛ nyɛ Aaron ne ne mma dea; akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron a ɛfiri AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ mu ne no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Aduane afɔdeɛ a mode bɛbrɛ AWURADE no nyinaa, mommfa mmɔreka nnyɛ; na monnhye mmɔreka biara ne ɛwoɔ biara sɛ ogya afɔdeɛ mmma AWURADE.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Momfa nnoɔma yi mmrɛ AWURADE sɛ aba a ɛdi kan mu afɔrebɔdeɛ, nanso wɔmmfa bi mmma afɔrebukyia no so sɛ ɛmmɛyi hwa hwanhwam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na w’aduane afɔdeɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ nyinaa, to mu nkyene, na mma wo Nyankopɔn apam nkyene mmpa w’aduane afɔdeɛ mu; fa nkyene ka w’ayɛyɛdeɛ nyinaa ho.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ wode aba a ɛdi kan ayɛyɛdeɛ rebrɛ AWURADE a, fa aburoo mmɛtem a wɔato no ogya mu atutu apɔn ho yɛ w’aba a ɛdi kan mu ayɛyɛdeɛ;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na fa ngo gu so, na fa ohwamfufuo to so; aduane afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye aburoo mfuamfua a wɔapɔn ho no bi ne ngo no bi ne ohwamfufuo no nyinaa sɛ nkaeɛ adeɛ; ɛyɛ ogya afɔdeɛ a wɔbɔ ma AWURADE."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na sɛ obi ayɛyɛdeɛ yɛ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, na anantwie no bi na ɔde reba a, onini oo, ɔbedeɛ oo, deɛ ɔdi mu na ɔmfa no mmra AWURADE anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔmfa ne nsa nto n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no atifi, na ɔnku no, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na Aaron mma no, asɔfoɔ no, mfa mogya no mpete afɔrebukyia no so nhyia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔnyi asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ no bi mmra mmɛyɛ AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ; sradeɛ a ɛkata ayamdeɛ no soɔ no ne ayamdeɛ no ho sradeɛ nyinaa,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ne sawa mmienu no ne sradeɛ a ɛwɔ ho, sisia mu no, ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no; ɔmfiri sawa ho nyi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Aaron mma no nhye no afɔrebukyia no so, mpae ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a ɛgu ogya no so, na ɛnyɛ ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ a ɔde rebɛbɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE no yɛ nnwan no bi a, onini oo, ɔbedeɛ oo, deɛ ɔdi mu na ɔmfa mmra.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ yɛ adwammaa na ɔde reba a, ɔmfa mmra AWURADE anim;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔmfa ne nsa nto n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no atifi, na ɔnku no ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na Aaron mma no mfa ne mogya mpete afɔrebukyia no so nhyia.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔnyi asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ no bi mmra mmɛbɔ ogya afɔdeɛ mma AWURADE; ne sradeɛ ne ne sradeɛ duapuo a ɔntwa no padua so pa ara ne sradeɛ a ɛkata ayamdeɛ soɔ ne ayamdeɛ ho sradeɛ nyinaa,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ne sawa mmienu no ne sradeɛ a ɛwɔ ho, sisia mu no, ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no; ɔmfiri sawa ho nyi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye no afɔrebukyia no so: Ɛyɛ aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔbɔ no gya so ma AWURADE.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no yɛ abirekyie a, ɔmfa mmra AWURADE anim;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na ɔmfa ne nsa nto n’atifi, na ɔnku no, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na Aaron mma no mfa ne mogya mpete afɔrebukyia no so nhyia.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔnyi bi mmra mmɛyɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ, AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ: Sradeɛ a ɛkata ayamdeɛ soɔ no ne ayamdeɛ ho sradeɛ nyinaa;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ne sawa mmienu no, ne sradeɛ a ɛwɔ ho, sisia mu no, ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no; ɔmfiri sawa ho nyi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye no wɔ afɔrebukyia no so; ɛyɛ ogya afɔreduane a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam; sradeɛ no nyinaa yɛ AWURADE dea.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu ne mo tenabea nyinaa sɛ: Monnni sradeɛ anaa mogya biara."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ: Sɛ obi anhyɛda na ɔyɛ nnoɔma a AWURADE ahyɛ sɛ wɔnnyɛ no mu biara,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> sɛ nso ɔsɔfoɔ a wɔasra no ɔsɔfo panin yɛ bɔne ma ɔman no di so a, ɛnneɛ ne bɔne a ɔyɛeɛ nti ma no mfa nantwie ba onini a ɔdi mu mmrɛ AWURADE mmɛyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔmfa nantwinini no mmra ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, AWURADE anim, na ɔmfa ne nsa nto n’atifi, na ɔnku no, AWURADE anim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ a wɔasra no no mfa nantwie no mogya no bi nkɔ ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nsateaa mmɔ mogya no mu, na ɔmpete mogya no bi mprɛnson, AWURADE anim, kronkronbea ntwamutam no anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa mogya no bi nkeka aduhwamhyeɛ bukyia a ɛwɔ AWURADE anim, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan mu no mmɛn ho, na ɔnhwie nantwie no mogya nyinaa ngu ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia a ɛwɔ ahyiaeɛ ntomadan ano no ase.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔnyi bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwie no sradeɛ nyinaa mfiri ne ho; sradeɛ a ɛkata ayamdeɛ so ne ayamdeɛ ho sradeɛ nyinaa,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ne sawa mmienu no ne sradeɛ a ɛwɔ so, sisia mu no ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no; ɔmfiri sawa ho nyi,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> sɛdeɛ wɔyi firi asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ nantwie ho no; na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye no ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔmfa nantwinini no nwoma ne ne nam nyinaa ne ne ti ne ne nnyawa ne n’ayamdeɛ ne n’agyanan no,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nantwinini mu no nyinaa, mfiri nkɔ nsraban no akyi, deɛ ɛhɔ teɛ, deɛ wɔhwie nso guo, na ɔmfa ogya nhye no nnyina so; deɛ wɔhwie nso guo na wɔnhye no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ Israel asafo nyinaa fom, na asɛm no ahunta ɔman no ani so, na wɔyɛ nnoɔma a AWURADE ahyɛ sɛ wɔnnyɛ no mu bi, na wɔdi so,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na wɔhunu bɔne a wɔayɛ de afom no a, ɛnneɛ, asafo no mfa nantwie ba onini mmra mmɛyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na wɔmfa no mmra ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na asafo no mu mpanimfoɔ mfa wɔn nsa ngu nantwinini no atifi, na wɔnkum nantwie no, AWURADE anim.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ a wɔasra no no mfa nantwinini no mogya no bi nhyɛne ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na ɔmfa ne nsateaa mmɔ mogya no mu mfa mpete mprɛnson, AWURADE anim, ntwamutam no anim,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na ɔmfa mogya no bi nkeka afɔrebukyia a ɛsi AWURADE anim, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu, no mmɛn ho, na ɔnhwie mogya no nyinaa ngu ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia a ɛsi ahyiaeɛ ntomadan ano no ase.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔnyi ne sradeɛ nyinaa mfiri so, na ɔnhye no afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na sɛdeɛ ɔyɛɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini no, saa ara na wɔnyɛ yei nso; na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma wɔn, na wɔde bɛkyɛ wɔn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔmfa nantwinini no mfiri nkɔ nsraban no akyi, na ɔnhye no sɛdeɛ wɔhyee kane nantwinini no, asafo no bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sɛ otitire bi anhyɛ da na ɔyɛ nnoɔma a AWURADE ne Nyankopɔn ahyɛ sɛ wɔnnyɛ no nyinaa mu adeɛ baako, na ɔdi so, na sɛ wɔma no hunu ne bɔne a wayɛ no a,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ɛnneɛ, ɔmfa n’ayɛyɛdeɛ a ɛyɛ ɔpapo a ɔdi mu mmra;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na ɔmfa ne nsa nto ɔpapo no atifi, na ɔnku no deɛ wɔkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no wɔ AWURADE anim: Bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nsateaa mfa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no mogya no bi nkeka ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no mmɛn ho, na ɔnhwie ne mogya no ngu ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no ase.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔnhye ne sradeɛ nyinaa wɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no so sɛ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ sradeɛ no; na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, ne bɔne no ho, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na sɛ asase no so nkurɔfoɔ no mu biara anhyɛda na ɔyɛ nnoɔma a AWURADE ahyɛ sɛ wɔnnyɛ no mu adeɛ baako, na ɔdi so, na sɛ wɔma no hunu ne bɔne a wayɛ a,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ɛnneɛ, ne bɔne a wayɛ no nti, ɔmfa n’ayɛyɛdeɛ, abirekyibereɛ a ɔdi mu mmra mmɛma;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na ɔmfa ne nsa nto bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no atifi, na ɔnkum bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no deɛ wɔkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ hɔ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nsateaa nka mogya no bi nkeka ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no mmɛn ho, na ɔnhwie ne mogya nyinaa ngu ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no ase.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ɔnyi ɛho sradeɛ sɛdeɛ wɔyi asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ deɛ no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye no ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no so, na ɛnyi hwa hwanhwam mma AWURADE; na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na sɛ ɔde adwammaa bɛyɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ ba bɛbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ a, ɔmfa ɔbedeɛ a ɔdi mu mmra.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ɔmfa ne nsa nto bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no atifi, na ɔnku no nyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, deɛ wɔkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ hɔ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nsateaa nka bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no mogya no bi nkeka ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no mmɛn ho, na ɔnhwie mogya no nyinaa ngu afɔrebukyia no ase.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na ɔnyi ne sradeɛ nyinaa, sɛdeɛ wɔyi asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ adwammaa ho sradeɛ no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye no afɔrebukyia so, sɛdeɛ AWURADE gya afɔrebɔ teɛ no; na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, ne bɔne a wayɛ no ho, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na sɛ obi yɛ bɔne sɛ wate ntanka nne na ɔne ɛho danseni, sɛ ɔhunui oo, ɔtee oo, na wanka a, ɔbɛsoa ne mmusuo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Anaasɛ sɛ obi ka afideɛ biara, sɛ aboa bi a ne ho nteɛ funu, anaa afieboa bi a ne ho nteɛ funu, anaa aboaa bi a ne ho nteɛ funu, na ɔnnim mpo a, ne ho agu fi, na ɔdi so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Anaasɛ sɛ ɔka onipa ho fi bi, na sɛ afideɛ a ama oniiko ho agu fi no te sɛn ara, na ɔnnim mpo a, sɛ akyire yi ɔhunu a, ɔdi so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sɛ asɛnhunu firi onipa anomu anaasɛ ɔka ntam sɛ ɔbɛyɛ bɔne anaa papa bi na ɔnnim mpo a, sɛ akyire n’ani ba ne ho so a, ɔdi adeɛ yi mu biara ho so;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na afei sɛ ɔdi adeɛ yi mu biara ho so a, ɔnka deɛ wayɛ mu bɔne no,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ne bɔne a wayɛ no nti, ɔmfa n’asodie ho afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE, nnwan mu ɔbedeɛ, odwanten anaa abirekyie, na ɛnyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no wɔ ne bɔne no ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ ne nsa anso odwan so a, ɔmfa anyankuku mmienu anaa mmorɔnoma mma mmienu mmrɛ AWURADE mmɛyɛ bɔne a wayɛ no mu asodie ho afɔdeɛ; baako nyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na baako nyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔmfa mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no, na ɔmfa deɛ ɛyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no kane, na ɔnkyinsa ne ti, ne kɔn so, nanso ɔnnte mfiri so;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɔmfa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no mogya no bi mpete afɔrebukyia no ho, na mogya no nkaeɛ no ɔmfa ngu ɔhyeɛ afɔrebukyia no ase, bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na deɛ ɔtɔ so mmienu no, ɔmfa no mmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, sɛdeɛ ne yɛbea teɛ. Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no wɔ ne bɔne a wayɛ no ho, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ ne nsa anso anyankuku mmienu anaa mmorɔnoma mma mmienu so a, deɛ ɔmfa nyɛ ne bɔne a ɔyɛeɛ ho ayɛyɛdeɛ ne esiam olonka abupɛn du mu baako, na ɛnyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ; ɔmmfa ngo nngu so, na ɔmmfa ohwamfufuo nnto so, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔmfa mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa mu nsa ma nyɛ nkaeɛ adeɛ, na ɔnhye no afɔrebukyia no so, sɛdeɛ AWURADE gya afɔrebɔ teɛ no: Bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, ne bɔne a wayɛ nnoɔma yi biara mu no ho, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no; na nkaeɛ no nyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no deɛ, sɛ aduane afɔdeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ obi anhyɛ da yɛ bɔne a ɛyɛ kusumdie wɔ AWURADE akronkronneɛ ho a, ɛnneɛ, n’asodie afɔdeɛ a ɔmfa mmrɛ AWURADE ne odwennini a ɔdi mu, sɛdeɛ wobɛbɔ ne boɔ, dwetɛ nnwetɛbena mu, sɛdeɛ kronkronbea dwetɛbena teɛ; na ɛnyɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na deɛ wayɛ ɛho bɔne, akronkronneɛ mu no, ɔnsi ananmu, na ɔmfa mu abupɛn nnum mu baako mpae so, na ɔmfa mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa asodie ho afɔdeɛ dwennini no mpata mma no, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na sɛ obi yɛ bɔne yɛ nnoɔma a AWURADE ahyɛ sɛ wɔnnyɛ no mu adeɛ baako a, sɛ wanhunu mpo a, ɔdi so na ɔso ne mmusuo;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na ɔmfa odwennini a ɔdi mu mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no, sɛdeɛ wobɛbɔ ne boɔ, na ɛnyɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ; na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, fom a wafom na wanhunu no ho, na wɔde bɛkyɛ no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Asodie ho afɔdeɛ ne no. AWURADE ho so na wadie."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sɛ obi yɛ bɔne di AWURADE kusum sɛ ɔsane ne yɔnko adeɛ bi a ɔde ama no asie, anaasɛ ɔde ahyɛ ne nsa, anaasɛ ɔbɔ korɔno, anaasɛ ɔdi ne yɔnko amim,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> anaasɛ wahunu biribi a ayera na ɔsane, na ɔka ntanhunu, sɛ onipa yɛ yeinom biara mu bɔne,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> sɛ ɛba sɛ ɔyɛ bɔne na ɔdi so saa a, ɔmfa adeɛ a ɔfaeɛ anaa adeɛ a ɔdii mu amim, anaa adeɛ a wɔde maa no asie anaa adeɛ a ɛyeraeɛ a ɔhunuiɛ,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> anaa adeɛ biara a ɔkaa ɛho ntanhunu no nsane mmra, ɔmfa ne nyinaa mmra, na ɔmfa abupɛn nnum mu baako mpae so mma ɔdenadeɛ no, n’asodie ho afɔrebɔ da no ara;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ɔmfa n’asodie ho afɔdeɛ a ɔde rebrɛ AWURADE no mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no, nnwan mu odwennini a ɔdi mu, sɛdeɛ wobɛbɔ ne boɔ, na ɛnyɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no wɔ AWURADE anim, na wɔde adeɛ biara a wayɛ a ɔdi ho so no bɛkyɛ no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hyɛ Aaron ne ne mma no sɛ: Yei ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ho mmara: Ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no ntena asomurofi, afɔrebukyia no so anadwo mu nyinaa nkɔsi anɔpa, na wɔmma afɔrebukyia no so gya no nnɛre wɔ so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhyɛ ne nwera atadeɛ, na ɔnhyɛ ne nwera twakoto nkata ne ho, na ɔnsesa nso a ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ogya no hye gyaa no afɔrebukyia no soɔ no ngu afɔrebukyia no nkyɛn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔnyi ne ntadeɛ no, na ɔnhyɛ ntadeɛ foforɔ, na ɔmfa nso no mfiri nkɔ nsraban no akyi nkɔgu deɛ ɛhɔ teɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔmma afɔrebukyia so gya no nnɛre, ennnum ara da, na ɔsɔfoɔ no nsɔ nnyina wɔ so daa anɔpa, na ɔnsiesie ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no wɔ so, na ɔnhye so asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ho sradeɛ no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ogya nnɛre afɔrebukyia no so daa, ɛnnnum da.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yei ne aduane afɔdeɛ ho mmara: Aaron mma no mfa mmra AWURADE anim wɔ afɔrebukyia no anim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔmfa aduane afɔdeɛ no esiam no nsa ma ne ngo no bi ne aduane afɔdeɛ no so hwamfufuo nyinaa, na ɔnhye wɔ afɔrebukyia no so, na ɛnyi hwa hwanhwam nyɛ nkaeɛ adeɛ mma AWURADE.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na nkaeɛ no, Aaron ne ne mma no nni no apiti, wɔnni no deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no adihɔ na wɔnnie.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wɔmmfa mmɔreka mmfra nnto. Wɔn kyɛfa a mede mama wɔn wɔ me gya afɔdeɛ mu ne no; ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron, sɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne asodie ho afɔdeɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Aaron mma mu mmarima nyinaa nni; ɛnyɛ AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ ahodoɔ ho daa ahyɛdeɛ, mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu. Obiara a ɔka no nyɛ kronkron.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yei ne Aaron ne ne mma ayɛyɛdeɛ a wɔmfa mmrɛ AWURADE, ɛda a wɔsra no ngo no; esiam olonka abupɛn du mu baako nyɛ daa ayɛyɛdeɛ, anɔpa deɛ fa na anwummerɛ deɛ fa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Wɔmfa ngo nkye no dadeɛ ayowa mu; yɛ no nkyekyeewa bra; yɛ no sɛ aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔatoto abubu mu asinasini bra, na ɛnyi hwa hwanhwam mma AWURADE.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ a wɔbɛsra no ngo asi n’ananmu wɔ ne mma mu no na ɔnyɛ; ɛyɛ AWURADE daa ahyɛdeɛ; wɔnhye no mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no aduane afɔdeɛ nyinaa wɔnhye no mu; wɔnnni bi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Aaron ne ne mma no sɛ: Yei ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ho mmara: Faako a wɔkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ aboa no, ɛhɔ ara na wɔnkum bɔne ho afɔdeɛ deɛ no, AWURADE anim; akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron ne no.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no na ɔnnie; faako a ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron na wɔnni wɔ ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no adihɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Obiara a ɔka nam no nyɛ kronkron; na deɛ mogya no bi apete n’atadeɛ mu no nsi deɛ ɛpetee mu no wɔ deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ahina a wɔnoaa no wɔ mu no, wɔmmɔ, na sɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ sɛn mu na wɔnoaeɛ a, wɔntwi mu na wɔmfa nsuo nhohoro mu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Mmarima a wɔfiri asɔfoɔ abusuakuo mu nyinaa nni bi; ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na bɔne ho afɔdeɛ a wɔde ne mogya no bi ba ahyiaeɛ ntomadan mu bɛpata wɔ kronkronbea hɔ no nyinaa, wɔnnni, wɔmfa ogya nhye."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na yei ne asodie ho afɔdeɛ ho mmara; ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Faako a wɔkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ aboa no, ɛhɔ ara na wɔnkum asodie ho afɔdeɛ deɛ no nso; na ɔnhwie ne mogya mpete afɔrebukyia no so nhyia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔnyi ne sradeɛ nyinaa mmra: Ne sradedua, ne sradeɛ a ɛkata ayamdeɛ ho no,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ne sawa mmienu ne sradeɛ a ɛwɔ ho, sisia mu no, ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan, ɔmfiri sawa ho nyi;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye ne nyinaa afɔrebukyia no so nyɛ AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ; asodie ho afɔdeɛ ne no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mmarima a wɔfiri asɔfoɔ abusuakuo nyinaa nni; deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron na wɔnnie; ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ teɛ no, sɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ nso teɛ ne no, mmara korɔ na ɛda ho; ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔde pata no, ɛnyɛ ne dea.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ma obi no, ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a ɔbɔeɛ no nwoma nyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no dea.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔto no fononoo mu nyinaa ne deɛ wɔsiesie no kukuo mu ne ɛkyeɛ dadeɛ soɔ nyinaa, ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔde ba no na ɛnyɛ ne dea.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔagu so ngo anaa deɛ ɛyɛ wesee nyɛ Aaron mma nyinaa deɛ, obiara nnya sɛdeɛ ne yɔnko nya.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na yei ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ a wɔbɔ ma AWURADE no ho mmara.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sɛ wɔyɛ no aseda afɔdeɛ de ba a, aseda afɔdeɛ a ɔde ba no nyɛ apiti taterɛ a wɔde ngo afɔre, ne apiti ɔfam a wɔde ngo agu soɔ ne esiam taterɛ a wɔde ngo afɔre akyeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mmɔreka paanoo taterɛ na ɔmfa nka n’ayɛyɛdeɛ ne n’asomdwoeɛ aseda afɔdeɛ no ho mmra.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔmfa ayɛyɛdeɛ no mu biara baako mmra, na wɔmma so mma AWURADE, ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔde asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ mogya peteeɛ no na ɛnyɛ ne dea.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na n’asomdwoeɛ aseda afɔdeɛ no nam no, wɔnni no da a wɔde baeɛ no ara, wɔnnnya bi nnkɔsi adekyeeɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na sɛ n’ayɛyɛdeɛ no yɛ bɔhyɛ anaa ayamyi ayɛyɛdeɛ a, wɔnni no da a ɔbɔ n’afɔdeɛ no, na sɛ adeɛ kye bi so a, wɔnni ara;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na afɔdeɛ no nam a ɛbɛka akɔsi da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no, wɔmfa ogya nhye.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na sɛ obi di n’asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ nam no bi da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no a, ɛrensɔ ani, na wɔremmu mma deɛ ɔde baeɛ no, ɛyɛ akyiwadeɛ, na ɔkra a ɔbɛdi bie no bɛsoa ne mmusuo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na nam a aka biribi a ɛho nteɛ no, wɔnnni; wɔmfa ogya nhye. Na nam deɛ, obiara a ne ho teɛ nni,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> nanso ɔkra a ɔbɛdi asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ nam a ɛyɛ AWURADE dea no bie, na n’afideɛ da ne soɔ no, wɔbɛtwa saa ɔkra no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔkra bi a ɔbɛka afideɛ biara, onipa ho afideɛ bi oo, aboa a ne ho nteɛ oo, akyiwadeɛ biara a ɛho nteɛ oo, na ɔbɛdi AWURADE asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ nam no bie no, wɔbɛtwa saa ɔkra no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ: Nantwie ne odwanten ne abirekyie sradeɛ biara, monnni.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na aboa funu sradeɛ ne deɛ wɔatete no sradeɛ, wɔmfa nyɛ adwuma biara, na die na monnnie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na obiara a ɔbɛdi afieboa a wɔde bi bɛbɔ AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ sradeɛ no, wɔbɛtwa ɔkra a ɔdie no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mogya biara nso, anomaa deɛ oo, atɔteboa deɛ oo, monnni wɔ mo tenabea biara mu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɔkra biara a ɔbɛdi mogya biara no, wɔbɛtwa saa ɔkra no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ: Deɛ ɔbɛbɔ n’asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE no, ɔmfa n’asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ no mu ayɛyɛdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ɔno ara ne nsa na ɔmfa nsɔ AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ no mu mmra, sradeɛ ne ɔyan na ɔmfa mmra; ɔyan no, wɔnhim nyɛ ohim afɔdeɛ AWURADE anim.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye sradeɛ no, afɔrebukyia no so, na ɔyan no nyɛ Aaron ne ne mma dea.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɔsrɛ nifa no, momfa nyɛ mo asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ mu mmasoɔ adeɛ mma ɔsɔfoɔ no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Aaron mma mu deɛ ɔde asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ mogya ne sradeɛ ba no, ɔno na ɔsrɛ nifa no nyɛ ne kyɛfa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ohim yan ne mmasoɔ srɛ no na mafa, Israelfoɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ no mu, na mede mama Ɔsɔfoɔ Aaron ne ne mma sɛ wɔn daa kyɛfa a ɛfiri Israel mma nsam.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Yei ne Aaron kyɛfa ne ne mma kyɛfa a ɛfiri AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ mu, ɛda a wɔde wɔn baa sɛ wɔmmɛdi AWURADE asɔfoɔ",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> na AWURADE hyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa mma wɔn, ɛda a wɔsraa wɔn ngo firii Israelfoɔ mu, sɛ ɛnyɛ wɔn daa kyɛfa, wɔn awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu no.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aduane afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne asodie ho afɔdeɛ ne atuhoakyɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> a AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose, Sinai bepɔ soɔ, ɛda a ɔhyɛɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ wɔmfa wɔn ayɛyɛdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE, Sinai serɛ soɔ no."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Fa Aaron ne ne mma ka ne ho, ɛne ntadeɛ no ne sra ngo no, ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini no ne adwennini mmienu no ne apiti kɛntɛn no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ma asafo no nyinaa mmɔ dwa, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Mose yɛɛ sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ no no, na ɔmaa asafo no bɔɔ dwa, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Mose ka kyerɛɛ asafo no sɛ: Yei ne adeɛ a AWURADE ahyɛ sɛ wɔnyɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Mose de Aaron ne ne mma no bae, na ɔde nsuo hohoroo wɔn ho;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na ɔde atadeɛ yuu no hyɛɛ no, na ɔde aboomu no bɔɔ n’asene, na ɔde batakari no hyɛɛ no, na ɔde asɔfotadeɛ no hyɛɛ no, na ɔde asɔfotadeɛ no nkyekyeremu no bɔɔ no abɔsoɔ;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔde adaaboɔ no hyehyɛɛ no, na ɔde Urim ne Tumim no hyɛɛ adaaboɔ no mu;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɔde abotitene no bɔɔ ne ti, na ɔde sikaterɛ no, kronkronyɛ ahyehyɛdeɛ no, fam abotitene no anim sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Mose faa sra ngo no de sraa tenabea no ne deɛ ɛwɔ mu nyinaa, na ɔyɛɛ no kronkron;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɔde bi petee afɔrebukyia no so mprɛnson, na ɔsraa afɔrebukyia no ne ɛho nnoɔma nyinaa ne kuduo no ne ntaaseɛ no ngo de yɛɛ no kronkron.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔhwiee sra ngo no bi guu Aaron atifi sraa no ngo de yɛɛ no kronkron.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Mose de Aaron mma no nso bae, na ɔhyehyɛɛ wɔn ntadeɛ, na ɔde aboomu bobɔ wɔn mu, na ɔde abotire bobɔɔ wɔn, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔmaa wɔde bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini no bae, na Aaron ne ne mma no de wɔn nsa guu bɔne afɔdeɛ nantwinini no atifi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Mose kumm no, na ɔde ne nsateaa kaa mogya no bi kekaa afɔrebukyia no mmɛn ho hyiae, na ɔyii afɔrebukyia no ho bɔne, na ɔhwiee mogya no petee afɔrebukyia no ase de dwiraa sɛ ɔde repata so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔfaa sradeɛ a ɛwɔ ayamdeɛ no ho nyinaa ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no ne sawa mmienu no ne ɛho sradeɛ, na Mose hyee no afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na nantwinini no ara ne ne nwoma ne ne nam ne n’agyanan no, ɔde ogya hyee, nsraban no akyi, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔde ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ dwennini no bae, na Aaron ne ne mma de wɔn nsa guu odwennini no atifi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔkum no, na Mose hwiee mogya no petee afɔrebukyia no so hyiae,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na ɔtwitwaa odwennini no mu asinasini, na Mose too tire no ne asinasini no ne sradeɛ no mu gya.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na n’ayamdeɛ ne ne nnyawa no, ɔde nsuo hohoroo ho. Na Mose too odwennini mu no nyinaa mu gya, afɔrebukyia no so; ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ne no, AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ ne no, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔde odwennini a ɔtɔ so mmienu no, atuhoakyɛ afɔdeɛ dwennini no bae, na Aaron ne ne mma no de wɔn nsa guu odwennini no atifi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Mose kumm no, na ɔfaa ne mogya no bi de kaa Aaron aso nifa ano ne ne nsa nifa kokurobetie ne ne nan nifa kokurobetie ano.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔde Aaron mma no bae, na Mose de mogya no bi kekaa wɔn aso nifa ano ne wɔn nsa nifa kokurobetie ne wɔn nan nifa kokurobetie ano; na Mose hwiee mogya no petee afɔrebukyia no so hyiae.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔfaa sradeɛ no ne sradedua no ne sradeɛ a ɛwɔ ayamdeɛ no ho nyinaa ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no ne sawa mmienu no ne ɛho sradeɛ ne srɛ nifa no,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na ɔfaa apiti kɛntɛn a ɛsi AWURADE anim no mu apiti taterɛ baako ne ngo paanoo taterɛ baako ne ɔfam baako de guu sradeɛ ne srɛ nifa no so,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na ɔde ne nyinaa hyɛɛ Aaron ne ne mma no nsa, na ɔhim yɛɛ ohim afɔdeɛ, AWURADE anim.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Mose gyee wɔn nsam, na ɔtoo mu gya wɔ afɔrebukyia no so wɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no so de yɛɛ atuhoakyɛ afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam; Ɛyɛ ogya afɔdeɛ ma AWURADE.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Mose faa atuhoakyɛ afɔdeɛ dwennini no yan no, na ɔhim yɛɛ ohim afɔdeɛ AWURADE anim; ɛyɛɛ Mose dea, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Mose faa sra ngo no bi ne afɔrebukyia no so mogya no bi de petee Aaron ne ne ntadeɛ ne ne mma ne ne mma ntadeɛ nyinaa so de dwiraa Aaron ne ne ntadeɛ ne ne mma ne ne mma ntadeɛ no.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Mose ka kyerɛɛ Aaron ne ne mma no sɛ: Monnoa nam no ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na monni no hɔ ara, ɛne atuhoakyɛ afɔdeɛ kɛntɛn no mu paanoo no, sɛdeɛ mehyɛɛ sɛ: Aaron ne ne mma nnie no.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na nam ne paanoo no mu deɛ ɛbɛka no, momfa ogya nhye.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na mommfiri ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano nnanson nkɔsi da a mo atuhoakyɛ nna no bɛwie duro, ɛfiri sɛ, nnanson na wɔde rehyɛ mo asɔfoɔ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Sɛdeɛ wɔreyɛ no nnɛ da yi no, AWURADE na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔnyɛ mfa mpata mma mo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na montena ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano awia ne anadwo nnanson, na monwɛn sɛdeɛ AWURADE ahyɛ no, na moanwuwu, na saa na wɔahyɛ me.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na Aaron ne ne mma no dii nsɛm a AWURADE nam Mose so hyɛeɛ no nyinaa so."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no Mose frɛɛ Aaron ne ne mma no ne Israel mpanimfoɔ,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ Aaron sɛ: Fa nantwie ba a wode bɛyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne odwennini a wode bɛyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, wɔnni mu, na fa bra AWURADE anim.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israelfoɔ no nso, kasa kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Momfa ɔpapo mmɛyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne nantwie ba ne odwanten ba a wɔadi afe afe a wɔdi mu mmɛyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ne nantwinini ne odwennini mmɛyɛ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, na wɔmfa mmɔ afɔdeɛ AWURADE anim ne aduane afɔdeɛ a wɔagu so ngo, ɛfiri sɛ ɛnnɛ na AWURADE bɛyi ne ho akyerɛ mo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔde deɛ Mose hyɛeɛ no baa ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no anim, na asafo no nyinaa twe bae bɛgyinaa AWURADE anim.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Mose kaa sɛ: Yei ne asɛm a AWURADE hyɛeɛ no, monyɛ, na AWURADE animuonyam nyi ne ho nkyerɛ mo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Mose ka kyerɛɛ Aaron sɛ: Twe pini afɔrebukyia no ho, na bɔ wo hyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne wo bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na pata ma wo ho ne ɔman no; na fa ɔman no ayɛyɛdeɛ bra, na pata ma wɔn, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛeɛ no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Aaron twe pinii afɔrebukyia no ho, na ɔkum ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwie ba no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ne mma no de mogya no kɔmaa no, na ɔde ne nsateaa bɔɔ mogya no mu de kekaa afɔrebukyia no mmɛn ho, na ɔhwiee mogya no petee afɔrebukyia no ase.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no mu sradeɛ ne sawa ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no, ɔtoo mu gya, afɔrebukyia no so, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɛnam no ne nwoma no deɛ, ɔde ogya hyee no nsraban no akyi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔkumm ɔhyeɛ aboa afɔdeɛ no nso, na Aaron mma no de mogya no brɛɛ no, na ɔhwie petee afɔrebukyia no so hyiae.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔde ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no asinasini ne ne tiri no brɛɛ no, na ɔhyee no afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔhohoroo ayamdeɛ ne nnyawa no ho, na ɔhyee no ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a ɛwɔ afɔrebukyia no soɔ no so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛnna ɔde ɔman no afɔdeɛ no baeɛ, na ɔfaa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ papo a ɔyɛ ɔman no deɛ no kumm no de bɔɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ sɛ kane deɛ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔde ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no bae, na ɔbɛyɛɛ no sɛdeɛ ne yɛbea teɛ no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔde aduane afɔdeɛ no bae, na ɔfaa emu nsa ma hyee no afɔrebukyia no so kaa anɔpa ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ no ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna ɔkumm nantwinini ne odwennini a ɛyɛ ɔman no asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ no, na Aaron mma no de mogya no brɛɛ no, na ɔhwie petee afɔrebukyia no so hyiae.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na nantwinini ne odwennini no sradeɛ no, sradedua no ne deɛ ɛkata sawa ho no ne mmerɛboɔ so ntentan no,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> wɔde sradeɛ no nyinaa guu ɔyan no so, na wɔhyee sradeɛ no afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔyan no ne srɛ nifa no, Aaron him de yɛɛ ohim afɔdeɛ, AWURADE anim, sɛdeɛ Mose hyɛeɛ no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna Aaron maa ne nsa so kyerɛɛ ɔman no, na ɔhyiraa wɔn. Na ɔbɔɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ wieeɛ no, ɔsianee.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Mose ne Aaron hyɛnee ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu; na wɔfirii adie no, wɔhyiraa ɔman no. Ɛnna AWURADE animuonyam yii ne ho kyerɛɛ ɔman no nyinaa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ogya firii AWURADE anim bɛhyee afɔrebukyia no so ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne sradeɛ no. Na ɔman no nyinaa hunui, na wɔde anigyeɛ huroe, na wɔde wɔn anim butubutuu fam."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Aaron mma Nadab ne Abihu fefaa wɔn gyasɔ adeɛ, na wɔde ogya guguu mu, na wɔde aduhwam guguu so, na wɔde ananagya a ɔnhyɛɛ wɔn ho mmara baa AWURADE anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ogya firii AWURADE anim bɛhyee wɔn, na wɔwuwuu AWURADE anim.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Mose ka kyerɛɛ Aaron sɛ: Ɛno ne deɛ AWURADE kaa sɛ: Wɔn a wɔtwe pini me no mu na mɛyɛ me ho kronkron, na ɔman no nyinaa anim na mɛhyɛ me ho animuonyam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Aaron yɛɛ komm. Ɛnna Mose frɛɛ Aaron n’agya nuabarima Usiel mma Misael ne Elsafan baeɛ, na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Montwe mpini, na mommɛsoa mo nuanom no mfiri kronkronbea anim nkɔ nsraban no akyi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔtwe bae bɛsoaa wɔn, wɔn ntadeɛ mu, de wɔn kɔɔ nsraban no akyi sɛdeɛ Mose kaeɛ no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Mose ka kyerɛɛ Aaron ne ne mma Eleasa ne Itamar sɛ: Mommpɛsɛ mo ti, na monnsunsuane mo ntadeɛ mu, na moanwuwu, na abufuo amma asafo no nyinaa so, nanso mo nuanom, Israel fie nyinaa, nsu wɔn a AWURADE de ogya ahye wɔn yi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mommfiri ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano nso, na moanwuwu, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE sra ngo no wɔ mo so. Na wɔyɛɛ sɛdeɛ Mose kaeɛ no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Aaron sɛ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wo ne wo mma nyinaa, ansa na mobɛhyɛne ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu no, monnnom bobesa anaa nsa biara, na moanwuwu. Ɛnyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ, mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na moahunu ade kronkron ne adeɛ a ɛnyɛ kronkron ne adeɛ a ɛho teɛ ne deɛ ɛho nteɛ ntam nsonsonoeɛ,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na moakyerɛkyerɛ Israelfoɔ ahyɛdeɛ a AWURADE nam Mose so ka kyerɛɛ wɔn no nyinaa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Mose kasa kyerɛɛ Aaron ne ne mma Eleasa ne Itamar a wɔkaeɛ no sɛ: Momfa AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ mu aduane a ɛkaeɛ no, na monni no apiti, afɔrebukyia no ho, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Monni no deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron, na ɛyɛ AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ ho kyɛfa ma wo ne wo mma, ɛfiri sɛ saa na wɔahyɛ me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ohim yan no ne mmasoɔ srɛ no, monni no deɛ ɛhɔ teɛ, wo ne wo mmammarima ne wo mmammaa nyinaa, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ wo kyɛfa ne wo mma kyɛfa a wɔde ama mo afiri Israelfoɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mmasoɔ srɛ ne ohim yan no na wɔmfa nka sradeɛ a wɔhyeɛ no ho mmra, na wɔnhim no ohim afɔdeɛ, AWURADE anim, na ɛnyɛ wo deɛ ne wo mma deɛ nyɛ daa kyɛfa, sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛeɛ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na bɔne ho afɔdeɛ papo no, Mose hwehwɛɛ no brɛɛ ara yie, na hwɛ, wɔahye no. Na ne bo fuu Aaron mma Eleasa ne Itamar a wɔkaeɛ no, na ɔkaa sɛ:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Adɛn nti na moanni bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no wɔ kronkronbea hɔ? Ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron, na ɛno na wɔde ama mo, sɛ monsoa asafo no mmusuo no, na mompata mma wɔn, AWURADE anim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hwɛ, wɔamfa ne mogya no amma kronkronbea dan no mu; anka ɛsɛ sɛ modi no kronkronbea hɔ, sɛdeɛ mehyɛɛ mo no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Aaron kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ: Hwɛ, ɛnnɛ wɔde wɔn bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne wɔn hyeɛ afɔdeɛ aba AWURADE anim, na adeɛ a ɛte seyie abɛto me yi; na sɛ medi bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nnɛ a, ɛbɛsɔ AWURADE ani anaa?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Mose teeɛ no, n’akoma tɔɔ ne yam."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose ne Aaron see wɔn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Monkasa nkyerɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ: Yeinom ne mmoa a monni wɔ asase so mmoa nyinaa mu:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ntɔteboa mu wɔn a wɔwɔ tɔte a emu apaeɛ na wɔn tɔte mu apae koraa, na wɔpu deɛ wɔadie wesa no, ɛno na monnie.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Yeinom nko na monnnie, wɔn a wɔpu wesa anaa wɔn tɔte mu apaeɛ: Yoma, ɛfiri sɛ ɔpu wesa deɛ, nanso ne tɔte mu mpae, enti ne ho nte mma mo;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ne atwaboa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔpu wesa deɛ, nanso ne tɔte mu mpae, ne ho nte mma mo;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ne adanko, ɛfiri sɛ ɔpu wesa deɛ, nanso ne tɔte mu mpae, ne ho nte mma mo;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ne prako, ɛfiri sɛ ne tɔte mu apae koraa deɛ, nanso ɔmpu nwesa, ne ho nte mma mo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Monnni wɔn nam, na monnka wɔn afunu; wɔn ho nte mma mo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yei ne deɛ monnie deɛ ɛwɔ nsuo mu nyinaa mu: Deɛ ɛwɔ ntɛtɛ ne abon, nsuo mu, ɛpo ne nsuwansuwa mu, ɛnonom na monnie.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na biribiara a ɛnni ntɛtɛ ne abon, ɛpo ne nsuwansuwa mu, adeɛ a ɛwɔ nsuo mu nyinaa a nkwa wɔ mu nyinaa, ɛyɛ akyiwadeɛ ma mo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɛnyɛ mo akyiwadeɛ, monnni wɔn nam, na wɔn afunu nso, monkyi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Adeɛ biara a ɛnni ntɛtɛ ne abon wɔ nsuo mu no yɛ mo akyiwadeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na yeinom na monkyire ntuboa mu; monnni, wɔyɛ akyiwadeɛ: Ɔkɔdeɛ, ɔkɔrewa, ɔkomfufuo,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ɔkompɛtɛ, asansa, sɛdeɛ wɔn su teɛ,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ne anene ahodoɔ nyinaa,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> sohori, anadwo-akorɔma, ɛpo so asomfenakatakyi, akorɔma, sɛdeɛ wɔn su teɛ,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ne patubiaa, ɛpo so anene, patukɛseɛ,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bakanoma, nantwinoma, ɔpɛtɛ,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> sukɔnkɔn, asukɔnkɔn ahodoɔ, asɔkwaa ne apan.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ntuboa manyamanya a wɔnante nan nnan so nyinaa nyɛ akyiwadeɛ mma mo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nanso yeinom na monnie ntuboa nyinaa a wɔnante nan nnan soɔ nyinaa mu, wɔn a wɔwɔ aprɛ mmienu wɔ wɔn nan soɔ a wɔde hurihuri asase so no;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> wɔn mu deɛ monnie nie: Ntutummɛ ahodoɔ, nketekyire ahodoɔ, mfuntie ahodoɔ, mmɛbɛ ahodoɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ntuboa manyamanya a wɔwɔ nan nnan nyinaa yɛ akyiwadeɛ ma mo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na yeinom na mode gu mo ho fi; obiara a ɔka wɔn afunu no ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na obiara a ɔsoa wɔn afunu no, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ntɔteboa a wɔn tɔte mu apaeɛ, nanso emu nwie paeɛ na wɔmpu nwesa no nyinaa ho nte mma mo; obiara a ɔka wɔn no, ne ho nte.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na mmoa a wɔnam nan nnan soɔ nyinaa mu wɔn a wɔnam wɔn nsa ne wɔn nan mu no, wɔn ho nte mma mo; obiara a ɔka wɔn funu no, ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na deɛ ɔsoa wɔn funu bi no nsi ne ntadeɛ, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ; wɔn ho nte mma mo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na mmoa a wɔwea asase soɔ mu wɔn a wɔn ho nte mma mo nie: Ahweaa, akura, ne nkoterɛ ahodoɔ;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ne hwinamanhwan, ɔmampam, ɔkoterɛ, bɔmɔte ne abosomakoterɛ.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Yeinom ne wɔn a wɔn ho nte mma mo, mmoa a wɔwea nyinaa mu; sɛ wɔwu a, obiara a ɔka wɔn no, ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na adeɛ biara a wɔn mu bi awu atɔ soɔ no, ɛho nte: Dua adeɛ biara oo, atadeɛ oo, nwoma oo, awere oo, adeɛ biara a wɔde yɛ adwuma; wɔmfa nhyɛ nsuo mu, na ɛho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ ansa na ɛho ate.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na kukuo biara a wɔn mu bi bɛhwe mu no, deɛ ɛwɔ mu nyinaa ho nte, na kukuo no nso mommɔ no.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Aduane a wɔdie biara a nsuo no bi bɛgu mu no ho nte, na anonneɛ biara a wɔnom adeɛ biara a ɛte saa mu no ho nte.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na adeɛ biara a wɔn funu ho biribi bɛhwe soɔ, ɛho nte: Fononoo oo, bukyia oo, wɔmmubu: Ɛho nte, na mommu no sɛ ɛho nte.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Nanso nsuo aniwa anaa abura a nsuo wɔ mu deɛ, ɛho te ara; na biribiara a ɛka wɔn funu no, ɛho nte.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na sɛ wɔn funu bi hwe kuadeɛ a wɔdua biara so a, kuadeɛ no ho te;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> na sɛ wɔde nsuo gu kuadeɛ no so na wɔn afunu bi hwe so a, ɛho nte mma mo.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na sɛ mmoa a modie no bi wu a, deɛ ɔka ne funu no ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na deɛ ɔdi ne funu no bie no nsi ne ntadeɛ, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ; na deɛ ɔsoa ne funu no nsi ne ntadeɛ, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na adeɛ biara a ɛwea fam yɛ akyiwadeɛ, monnni.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Adeɛ biara a ɛnam yafunu soɔ ne adeɛ biara a ɛnam nan nnan so kɔsi adeɛ biara a ɛwɔ nan bebree soɔ, wɔn a wɔwea fam nyinaa mu no, monnni, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ akyiwadeɛ.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Monnyɛ mo ho akyiwadeɛ wɔ mmoa a wɔwea no biara ho, na monnyɛ mo ho fi a ɛmma mo ho nteɛ wɔ wɔn ho.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, enti monte mo ho na monyɛ kronkron, ɛfiri sɛ meyɛ kronkron; enti mommma mo kra ho nnkum, adeɛ biara a ɛwea a ɛtwe ne ho ase no ho.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na mene AWURADE a meyii mo Misraim asase so sɛ mɛyɛ mo Nyankopɔn no; enti monyɛ kronkron, ɛfiri sɛ meyɛ kronkron.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Yei ne aboa biara a wɔwɔ nsuo mu ne nnomaa ne aboa biara a wɔwea fam nyinaa ho mmara,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> sɛ wɔmfa mpae adeɛ a ɛho nteɛ ne deɛ ɛho teɛ mu, ne mmoa a wɔdie ne mmoa a wɔnnie mu."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛ: Sɛ ɔbaa bi nyinsɛn na ɔwo ɔbabanin a, ne ho nte nnanson te sɛ ne nsabuo nna mu a ne ho nteɛ no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, wɔntwa abɔfra no twetia.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔntena tannan mu adaduasa nnammiɛnsa n’ahodwira mogya mu; ɔnnka ade kronkron biara na ɔmmma kronkronbea hɔ kɔsi sɛ n’ahodwira nna bɛwie duro.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ ɔwo ɔbaa a, ne ho nte nnawɔtwe mmienu sɛ ne nsabuo nna mu, na ɔntena tannan mu adaduosia nnansia n’ahodwira mogya mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ ahodwira nna no wie du ma ɔbabanin anaa ɔbabaa no a, ɔmfa odwanten ba a wadi afe a wɔde bɛbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aborɔnoma ba anaa anyankuku a wɔde bɛbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ mmra ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano mmɛma ɔsɔfoɔ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔmfa mmra AWURADE anim, na ɔmpata mma no, na ne ho nte mfiri ne mogyaguo no mu. Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma ɔbaa a wawo ɔbabarima anaa ɔbabaa no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na sɛ ne nsa anso odwan ba so a, ɔmfa anyankuku mmienu anaa mmorɔnoma mma mmienu mmra mmɛma, baako nyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, na baako nso nyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, na ne ho nte."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose ne Aaron sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sɛ biribi ba onipa honam wedeɛ mu, sɛ nsoa oo, ntwintwameeɛ oo, ntampeɛ oo, na ɛdidi ne honam wedeɛ mu yɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ a, wɔmfa no mmrɛ Ɔsɔfoɔ Aaron anaa ne mma, asɔfoɔ no mu baako.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ honam wedeɛ mu ntotɔeɛ no, na ntotɔeɛ no so nwi adane fitaa, na ntotɔeɛ no atotɔ mu asene ne honam wedeɛ no a, ɛyɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ; na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ no a, ɔmmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na sɛ ɛyɛ ne honam wedeɛ mu ntampeɛ fitaa, na sɛ wɔhwɛ na ɛntotɔ mu nsene ne wedeɛ no, na ɛso nwi nnanee fitaa a, ɛnneɛ, ɔsɔfoɔ no nto ɔyarefoɔ no mu nnanson.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛda a ɛtɔ so nson no, ɔsɔfoɔ no nhwɛ, na sɛ ɔhunu sɛ ntotɔeɛ no te sɛdeɛ ɛteɛ n’ani so na ɛnyerɛɛ ne wedeɛ mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no nto no mu nnanson bio.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ no da a ɛtɔ so nson no bio na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no ani adum na ɛntrɛɛ ne wedeɛ mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no sɛ deɛ ne ho teɛ, ɛyɛ ntwintwameeɛ; na ɔnsi n’atadeɛ na ne ho ate.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nanso ɔde ne ho akɔkyerɛ ɔsɔfoɔ wɔ n’ahoteɛ ho no akyiri no, sɛ ntwintwameeɛ no yerɛ ne wedeɛ mu a, wɔmma ɔsɔfoɔ no nhwɛ no bio;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na hwɛ, ntwintwameeɛ no ayerɛ wedeɛ no mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ; ɛyɛ kwata.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ wɔ onipa bi ho a, wɔmfa no mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na hwɛ, nsoa fitaa bi wɔ wedeɛ no mu a adane nwi no fitaa, na ɛnam mono repu nsoaeɛ no mu a,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ɛyɛ kwata dada a ɛwɔ ne honam wedeɛ mu, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no sɛ ne ho nte. Ɔnnto no mu; na ne ho nte.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na sɛ kwata no apue afiri wedeɛ mu akata ɔyarefoɔ no honam nyinaa firi n’atifi kɔsi ne nan ase, baabiara a ɔsɔfoɔ no ani bɛhwɛ no,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na kwata no akata ne honam nyinaa so a, ɔmmu ɔyarefoɔ no sɛ ne ho te; ne ho nyinaa adane fitaa a, ne ho te.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nanso berɛ biara a wɔbɛhunu ne ho ɛnam mono no, ne ho nte.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ɛnam mono no a, ɔmmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ; ɛnam mono no ho nte, ɛyɛ kwata.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na sɛ ɛnam mono no sane dane fitaa, na ɔba ɔsɔfoɔ no nkyɛn,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no adane fitaa a, ɛnneɛ, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho teɛ; ne ho ate.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Sɛ mpɔmpɔ si obi honam wedeɛ mu na ɛsa,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na soa fitaa bi anaa ntampeɛ fitaa a ɛbereɛ ba mpɔmpɔ no ananmu a, wɔmma ɔsɔfoɔ no nhwɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ɛhɔ atotɔ mu asene wedeɛ no na emu nwi adane fitaa a, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ; ɛyɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ, apue wɔ mpɔmpɔ no mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ na sɛ nwi fitaa bi nni mu, na ɛntotɔɔ mu nsenee wedeɛ no na ani dum a, ɔsɔfoɔ no nto no mu nnanson;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na sɛ ɛyerɛ wedeɛ no mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ: Ɛyɛ ntotɔeɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na sɛ ntampeɛ no te sɛdeɛ ɛteɛ na ɛnyerɛe a, ɛyɛ mpɔmpɔ no twa, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho teɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Anaasɛ ogya kuro bi ba honam wedeɛ no mu, na ekuro no so bɔn repu yɛ ntampeɛ a ɛhoa fitaa na emu gyegyeɛ anaasɛ ɛhoa fitaa,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntampeɛ no mu nwi adane fitaa na wɔhwɛ a atotɔ mu asene wedeɛ no a, ɛyɛ kwata, na apue ogya kuro no mu, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ: Ɛyɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ enwi fitaa nni ntampeɛ no mu, na ɛntotɔɔ mu nsenee wedeɛ no, na ani dum a, ɔsɔfoɔ no nto no mu nnanson.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nson no, ɔsɔfoɔ no hunu sɛ ayerɛ wedeɛ no mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ: Ɛyɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na sɛ ntampeɛ no te sɛdeɛ ɛteɛ na ɛnyerɛe wɔ wedeɛ no mu na ani dum a, ɛyɛ soa a ogya kuro no asoa, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho teɛ; na ɛyɛ ogya kuro no bɔn.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ɔbarima anaa ɔbaa bi, sɛ biribi tɔ n’atifi anaa ne bɔgyesɛ mu,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ntotɔeɛ no, na sɛ atɔ mu asene wedeɛ no, na enwi kɔkɔɔ nhweanhweaa wɔ mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no sɛdeɛ ne ho nteɛ; ɛyɛ ntutuiɛ, ɛyɛ etire anaa bɔgyesɛ mu kwata.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ntutuiɛ ntotɔeɛ no, na sɛ ɛhɔ ntɔɔ mu nsenee wedeɛ no, na enwi tuntum nso nni mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no nto deɛ ntutuiɛ atotɔ no no mu nnanson.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ɔyarefoɔ no da a ɛtɔ so nson no, na sɛ ntutuiɛ no nyerɛe na enwi kɔkɔɔ mmaa mu, na ntutuiɛ no ntɔɔ mu nsenee wedeɛ no a,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ɔnyi ne ho nwi, na ɔnnyi ntutuiɛ no so, na ɔsɔfoɔ no nto deɛ ntutuiɛ ayɛ no no mu nnanson bio.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ntutuiɛ no da a ɛtɔ so nson no, na sɛ ntutuiɛ no nyerɛɛ wedeɛ no mu na ɛhɔ ntɔɔ mu nsenee wedeɛ no a, ɛnneɛ, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho teɛ; na ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ne ho ate.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na sɛ ɛno akyi, ntutuiɛ no yerɛ,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ no, na sɛ ntutuiɛ no ayerɛ wedeɛ no mu a, ɔsɔfoɔ no nnhwehwɛ enwi kɔkɔɔ; ne ho nte.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na sɛ ɔhunu ntutuiɛ no sɛ ɛte sɛdeɛ ɛteɛ na enwi tuntum afu mu a, na ntutuiɛ no asa; ne ho te, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho teɛ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na sɛ ntampeɛ fitaa ba ɔbarima anaa ɔbaa wedeɛ ani,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntampeɛ a ani dum fitaa wɔ wɔn honam wedeɛ mu a, ɛyɛ ɛyam a ayerɛ wedeɛ mu; ne ho te.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na sɛ ɔbarima bi tiri pa a, ɔyɛ atipa; ne ho te.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na sɛ n’apampam anim fam na apa a, ɔyɛ atipa; ne ho te.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na sɛ biribi fitaa a ɛbereɛ tɔ n’atipa no mu anaasɛ n’apampam paeɛ no mu a, ɛyɛ kwata a ɛrepue n’atipa anaa n’apampam paeɛ no mu.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ fitaa a ɛbereɛ asoa n’atipa no anaa n’apampam paeɛ no mu a ɛte sɛ honam wedeɛ mu kwata a,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> ɔyɛ ɔkwatani; ne ho nte; buo na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu no deɛ ne ho nteɛ; ne tiri so na ne ntotɔeɛ no wɔ.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na ɔkwatani a yadeɛ no wɔ ne ho nsunsuane ne ntadeɛ mu, na ɔmpɛsɛ ne ti, na ɔnkata ne soro anofafa, na ɔnteam sɛ: Me ho nte, me ho nte!",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Nna dodoɔ a yadeɛ no wɔ ne ho no, teɛ na ne ho nteɛ; ɔno nko na ɔntena, nsraban no akyi na ɔntena.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Na sɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ wɔ atadeɛ bi mu, sɛ ɛwɔ kuntutam anaa asaawatam,",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> anaa nsa anaa mfa a wɔde nwono asaawatam anaa kuntutam anaa nwoma anaa adeɛ biara a wɔde nwoma ayɛ mu,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no biri anaasɛ ɛbere ntoma anaa nwoma no anaa nsa anaa mfa no anaa adeɛ biara a wɔde nwoma ayɛ mu a, ɛyɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ, wɔmma ɔsɔfoɔ no nhwɛ.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ntotɔeɛ no a, ɔnto adeɛ a ntotɔeɛ no wɔ mu no mu nnanson.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Na ɛda a ɛtɔ so nson no, ɔhunu sɛ ntotɔeɛ no ayerɛ atadeɛ no anaa nsa anaa mfa anaa nwoma no anaa biribiara a wɔde nwoma ayɛ no mu a, na ntotɔeɛ no yɛ kwata a ɛsɛe adeɛ; ɛho nte.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Na ɔnhye ntoma no, sɛ nsa no anaa mfa no oo, anaa kuntu anaa asaawa anaa nwoma adeɛ biara mu na ntotɔeɛ no wɔ oo, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ kwata a ɛsɛe adeɛ. Ogya na wɔmfa nhyeɛ.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no nterɛɛ atadeɛ no mu wɔ nsa anaa mfa anaa nwoma adeɛ biara mu a,",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> ɛnneɛ, ɔsɔfoɔ no nhyɛ na wɔnsi adeɛ a ntotɔeɛ no wɔ mu no, na ɔnto mu nnanson bio.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Na ntotɔeɛ no sie akyiri no ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no ani nsakyerae na ɛnyerɛe nso a, ɛho nte, wɔmfa ogya nhye; ani akuku oo, akyire akuku oo, ɛyɛ nweweeɛ.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Na sɛ ne sie akyiri no ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no ani dum a, ɔnte mfiri ntoma no anaa nsa anaa mfa no mu.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Na sɛ wɔhunu bio wɔ ntoma no mu wɔ nsa anaa mfa anaa nwoma adeɛ biara mu a, ɛyɛ kwata a ɛrepue, wɔmfa ogya nhye deɛ ntotɔeɛ no wɔ mu no.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Na ntoma no, mfa anaa nsa anaa nwoma adeɛ biara a wɔbɛsie na ntotɔeɛ no bɛfiri mu no, wɔnsi bio na ɛho ate.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma kwata ntotɔeɛ, kuntutam anaa asaawatam anaa nsa anaa mfa anaa nwoma adeɛ biara mu, na wɔde abu no adeɛ a ɛho teɛ anaa adeɛ a ɛho nteɛ."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma ɔkwatani, ɛda a wɔbu no sɛ ne ho ateɛ no. Wɔmfa no mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfiri adi nkɔ nsraban no akyi; na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ na sɛ kwata ntotɔeɛ no asa ɔkwatani no ho a,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ɔsɔfoɔ no nhyɛ mma wɔmfa nnomaa a wɔn ho teɛ mmienu animono ne tweneduro dua ne koogyan ne adwera mma deɛ wɔrebɛte ne ho no mmra.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhyɛ mma wɔnkum nnomaa no mu baako, ayowa bi mu, mmasuo so.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na anomaa nikanfoɔ no deɛ, ɔmfa no ne tweneduro dua no ne koogyan ne adwera no, na ɔmfa ne nyinaa ne anomaa nikanfoɔ no mmɔ anomaa a wɔaku no mmasuo soɔ no mogya mu,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na ɔmfa mpete deɛ ɔbɛte ne ho afiri ne kwata ho no so mprɛnson, na ɔnte ne ho, na ɔnnyaa anomaa nikanfoɔ no mma no nkɔ wiram.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na deɛ wɔate ne ho no nsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔnyi ne nwi nyinaa koraa, na ɔmfa nsuo nnware na ne ho ate; na ɛno akyiri no ɔmmra nsraban no mu, nanso ɔntena ne ntomadan akyi nnanson.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nson no, ɔnyi ne ho nwi nyinaa, ne tiri ne ne bɔgyesɛ ne n’anintɔnnwi nyinaa na ɔnyie; na ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ, na ɔmfa nsuo nnware ne honam, na ne ho ate.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɛda a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, ɔmfa nnwanten mma mmienu a wɔdi mu, ne odwammaa bedeɛ baako a wadi afe a ɔdi mu, ne aduane afɔdeɛ esiam efa abupɛn du mu mmiɛnsa a wɔde ngo afɔre, ne ngo toa ma baako mmra.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ a ɔte ne ho no mfa ɔbarima a wɔrete ne ho no ne nnoɔma no mmɛgyina AWURADE anim, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa nnwanten no mu baako mmra, sɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ ne ngo toa ma no, na ɔnhim no ohim afɔdeɛ, AWURADE anim;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na ɔnkum odwanten ba no deɛ wɔkum bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ hɔ, deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron, ɛfiri sɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ no nso yɛ asɔfoɔ no dea, te sɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa asodie ho afɔdeɛ mogya no bi nkeka deɛ wɔrete ne ho no aso nifa ne ne nsa nifa kokurobetie ne ne nan nifa kokurobetie ano.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ngo toa no mu bi nhwie ngu ɔno ara ne nsa benkum mu;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nsateaa nifa mmɔ ngo a ɛwɔ ne nsa benkum mu no mu, na ɔmfa ne nsateaa nka ngo no bi mpete mprɛnson, AWURADE anim;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na ngo a ɛbɛka ne nsam no, ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa bi nkeka deɛ wɔrete ne ho no aso nifa ne ne nsa nifa kokurobetie ne ne nan nifa kokurobetie ano, asodie ho afɔdeɛ mogya no so;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na ngo a ɛbɛka ɔsɔfoɔ no nsam no, ɔnhwie ngu deɛ wɔrete ne ho no atifi, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, AWURADE anim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no, na ɔmpata mma deɛ wɔrete ne ho afiri ne ho fi mu no; na ɛno akyiri no, ɔnkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ aboa no;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhye ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aduane afɔdeɛ no afɔrebukyia no so, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no na ne ho ate.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na sɛ ɔdi hia na ne nsa anso yeinom so a, ɛnneɛ ɔmfa odwanten ba baako mmɛyɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ nyɛ ohim afɔdeɛ mfa mpata mma no, ne aduane afɔdeɛ esiam olonka abupɛn du mu baako a wɔde ngo afɔre, ne ngo toa ma",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ne anyankuku mmienu anaa mmorɔnoma mma mmienu a ne nsa bɛso soɔ; baako nyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ na baako nyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na n’ahodwira da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, ɔmfa mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, AWURADE anim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa asodie ho afɔdeɛ dwanten ba no ne ngo toa ma no, na ɔnhim no ohim afɔdeɛ, AWURADE anim.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔnkum asodie ho afɔdeɛ dwanten ba no, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa asodie ho afɔdeɛ mogya no bi nkeka deɛ wɔrete ne ho no aso nifa ne ne nsa nifa kokurobetie ne ne nan nifa kokurobetie ano;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ngo no ngu ɔno ara ne nsa benkum mu,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ne nsateaa nifa nka ngo a ɛwɔ ne nsa benkum mu no bi mpete mprɛnson, AWURADE anim;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa ngo a ɛwɔ ne nsam no bi nkeka deɛ wɔrete ne ho no aso nifa ne ne nsa nifa kokurobetie ne ne nan nifa kokurobetie ano, deɛ asodie ho afɔdeɛ no mogya no wɔ no;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na ngo a ɛbɛka ɔsɔfoɔ no nsam no, ɔnhwie ngu deɛ wɔrete ne ho no atifi mfa mpata mma no, AWURADE anim.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɔmfa anyankuku anaa mmorɔnoma mma a ne nsa bɛso soɔ no mu baako,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> adeɛ a ne nsa bɛso soɔ no mu baako nyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na baako nyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ mpae aduane afɔdeɛ no so, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma deɛ wɔrete ne ho no, AWURADE anim.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma deɛ kwata atotɔ no a ne nsa nso n’ahodwira adeɛ soɔ no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose ne Aaron sɛ:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Sɛ moduru Kanaan asase a mede merema mo sɛ monni soɔ no so, na sɛ mede kwata ntotɔeɛ metotɔ mo dibea asase no so fie bi ho a,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ɛnneɛ efie no wura no mmra mmɛka nkyerɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no sɛ: Ɛyɛ me sɛ biribi a ɛte sɛ ntotɔeɛ wɔ me fie hɔ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhyɛ mma wɔnyi efie no mu nnoɔma mfiri adi ansa na ɔsɔfoɔ no ahyɛne mu akɔhwɛ ntotɔeɛ no, na efie no mu nnoɔma nyinaa ho angu fi; na ɛno akyiri no ɔsɔfoɔ no nhyɛne mu nkɔhwɛ efie no.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no hwɛ ntotɔeɛ no, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no wɔ efie no fasuo ho, nkekaeɛ apopobibire anaa kɔkɔɔ, na ani atotɔ mu asene ɔfasuo no a,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> ɔsɔfoɔ no mfiri efie no mu mmra ɛpono ano, na ɔnto efie no mu nnanson.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na sɛ ɛda a ɛtɔ so nson no ɔsɔfoɔ no sane ba, na ɔbɛhwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no ayerɛ efie no fasuo ho a,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ɔsɔfoɔ no mma wɔntutu aboɔ a ntotɔeɛ no wɔ mu no nto ngu kuro no akyi deɛ ɛhɔ nteɛ;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> na wɔnwewɛre efie no mu nhyia, na wɔmfa dɔteɛ a wɔwewɛreeɛ no nkɔgu kuro no akyi deɛ ɛhɔ nteɛ;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> na wɔmfa aboɔ foforɔ nhyehyɛ aboɔ no ananmu, na wɔmfa dɔteɛ foforɔ mma efie no ho.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na sɛ aboɔ no tutuo ne efie no ho wewerɛ ne ɛho ma akyiri no ntotɔeɛ no sane bɛpue efie no mu,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> na ɔsɔfoɔ no ba na ɔbɛhwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no ayerɛ efie no mu a, ɛyɛ efie no mu kwata a ɛsɛe adeɛ; ɛho nte.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Enti ɔnnwiri efie no ngu fam, n’aboɔ ne ne mpuna ne efie no ho dɔteɛ nyinaa, na ɔnsesa mfiri adi nkɔ kuro no akyi nkɔgu deɛ ɛhɔ nteɛ.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Na deɛ ɔbɛkɔ efie no mu nna a wɔato mu nyinaa no, ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> na deɛ ɔda efie hɔ no nsi ne ntadeɛ, na deɛ ɔdidi fie hɔ no nsi ne ntadeɛ.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na sɛ efie no ho ma akyi ɔsɔfoɔ no ba bɛhwɛ, na sɛ ntotɔeɛ no nyerɛɛ efie no mu a, ɛnneɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu efie no sɛ ɛho te, ɛfiri sɛ ntotɔeɛ no asa.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Na ɔmfa nnomaa mmienu ne tweneduro dua ne koogyan ne adwera nnwira efie no.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Na ɔnkum nnomaa no mu baako ayowa mu, mmasuo so,",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> na ɔmfa tweneduro dua ne adwera ne koogyan ne anomaa animono no mmɔ anomaa a wɔaku no no mogya ne mmasuo no mu, na ɔmfa mpete efie no ho mprɛnson,",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> na ɔmfa anomaa no mogya ne mmasuo ne anomaa animono no ne tweneduro dua ne adwera ne koogyan no nnwira efie no,",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> na ɔnnyaa anomaa animono no kuro no akyi mma no nkɔ wiram, na ɔmpata mma efie no, na ɛho ate.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma kwata ntotɔeɛ nyinaa ne ntutuiɛ,",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> ne ntoma ne efie ho kwata,",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> nsoa ne ntwintwameeɛ ne ntampeɛ,",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> sɛ ɛnkyerɛkyerɛ berɛ a adeɛ ho nteɛ ne berɛ a ɛho teɛ mu; yei ne kwata ho mmara."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose ne Aaron sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Monkasa nkyerɛ Israelfoɔ no nse wɔn sɛ: Ɔbarima biara sɛ ne ho sene gu a, n’ahosene no nti ne ho nte.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na deɛ ɛgu ne ho fi n’ahosene no mu nie: Sɛ n’ahosene firi ne honam anaasɛ n’ahosene ma ne honam ano si a, ɛyɛ ne ho figuo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mpa biara a deɛ ne ho sene no bɛda so no ho nte, na adeɛ biara a ɔbɛtena soɔ no ho nte.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na deɛ ɔka ne mpa no nsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na deɛ ɔtena adeɛ a deɛ ne ho sene no tenaa soɔ no, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na deɛ ɔka deɛ ne ho sene no honam no, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na sɛ deɛ ne ho sene no to ntasuo gu deɛ ne ho teɛ so a, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na aboa so adwa biara a ɔhosenefoɔ no bɛtena soɔ no ho nte; na obiara a ɔka biribiara a ɛwɔ ɔhosenefoɔ no ase no ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na deɛ ɔsoa saa adeɛ no nsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na obiara a ɔhosenefoɔ no amfa nsuo anhohoro ne nsa na ɔbɛka no no, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na kukuo a ɔhosenefoɔ no bɛka no, wɔmmɔ, na dua adeɛ biara deɛ, wɔmfa nsuo nhohoro ho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ ɔhosenefoɔ no ho te firi n’ahosene no mu a, ɔnkan nnanson ngu n’ahofire so, na ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ, na ɔmfa mmasuo nnware ne honam, na ne ho ate.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, ɔmfa anyankuku mmienu anaa mmorɔnoma mma mmienu mmra AWURADE anim, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na ɔmfa mma ɔsɔfoɔ no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa baako nyɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na baako no nso ɔmfa nyɛ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no AWURADE anim mfiri n’ahosene no mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na sɛ ɔbarima bi ahoba firi ne mu a, ɔmfa nsuo nnware ne honam nyinaa, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ntoma biara anaa nwoma biara a ahoba bɛgu mu no, wɔmfa nsuo nsi, na ɛho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na sɛ ɔbarima ne ɔbaa da na ahoba gu no a, wɔmfa nsuo nnware na wɔn ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔbaa sɛ ne ho sene na mogya firi ne honam mu gu a, ɔntena ne nsabuo no mu nnanson, na obiara a ɔka no no ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na adeɛ biara a ɔda soɔ ne nsabuo mu no ho nte, na adeɛ a ɔtena soɔ no ho nte.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na obiara a ɔka ne mpa no, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na obiara a ɔka adeɛ biara a watena soɔ no, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na sɛ biribi wɔ mpa no so anaasɛ adeɛ a watena soɔ no so a, obi ka a, ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na sɛ ɔbarima ne no da na ne nsabuo adeɛ no bi ka ne ho a, ne ho nte nnanson, na ne mpa a ɔda soɔ no nyinaa ho nte.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔbaa sɛ ne ho sene mogya gu nna pii, na ɛnyɛ ne nsabuo berɛ, anaasɛ ne ho sene tra ne nsabuo a, ɛnneɛ n’ahosene a ɛho nteɛ nna no nyinaa ne ho nte te sɛ ne nsabuo nna mu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ne mpa a ɔda soɔ biara n’ahosene nna nyinaa mu no nyɛ no sɛ ne nsabuo mpa, na adeɛ biara a ɔtena soɔ no ho nte sɛ ne nsabuo mu deɛ no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na obiara a ɔka nnoɔma yi no ho nte, na ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na sɛ ne ho te firi n’ahosene no mu a, ɔnkan nnanson mfa, na ɛno akyiri no ne ho ate.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no, ɔmfa anyankuku mmienu anaa mmorɔnoma mma mmienu mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa baako mmɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na baako no ɔmfa mmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mpata mma no, AWURADE anim, mfiri n’ahosene a ɛho nteɛ no mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na momma Israelfoɔ no nyi wɔn ho mfiri wɔn fi mu, na wɔanwuwu wɔn fi mu sɛ wɔrekɔgu me tenabea a ɛwɔ wɔn mu no ho fi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Yei ne mmara a ɛda hɔ ma deɛ ne ho sene ne deɛ ne ho nsuo firi ne mu gu ne ho fi,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> ne ɔbaa a ne ho nyɛ no den ne nsabuo mu, ne deɛ ne ho sene, ɔbarima oo, ɔbaa oo, ne ɔbarima a ɔne ɔbaa a ne ho nteɛ bɛda."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Aaron mma baanu no wuo a wɔbaa AWURADE anim na wɔwuiɛ no akyiri no, AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Kasa kyerɛ wo nua Aaron sɛ ɔnnhyɛne kronkronbea hɔ nnkɔ ntwamutam no akyi mpata adwa a ɛwɔ adaka no soɔ no anim berɛ nyinaa mu, na wanwu, ɛfiri sɛ mununkum no mu na meyi me ho mekyerɛ, mpata adwa no so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na yei ne deɛ Aaron mfa nhyɛne kronkronbea hɔ: Nantwininiburuwa a wɔde bɛbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne odwennini a wɔde bɛbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɔnhyɛ nwera atadeɛ kronkron no, na nwera twakoto nkata ne ho, na nwera aboomu no mmɔ n’asene, na ɔmmɔ nwera abotitene no, yei ne ntade kronkron no; ɔmfa nsuo nnware ne ho ansa na wahyɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔnnye Israel asafo no hɔ mpapo mmienu, na wɔmfa mmɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, ne odwennini baako, na wɔmfa mmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Aaron mfa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini a ɛyɛ ne deɛ no mmra, na ɔmfa mpata mma ɔno ara ne ho ne ne fie.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔmfa mpapo mmienu no mmɛgyina AWURADE anim, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Aaron ntwe mpapo mmienu no so tonto, AWURADE tonto baako ne Asasel tonto baako.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Aaron mfa ɔpapo a AWURADE tonto bɔɔ no no mmra mmɛbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔpapo a Asasel tonto bɔɔ no no, ɔmfa no animono nnyina AWURADE anim mfa mpata mma no na wɔnkɔgya no nkɔ serɛ so mma Asasel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Aaron mfa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini a ɛyɛ ne deɛ no mmra mfa mpata mma ɔno ara ne ho ne ne fie, na ɔnkum bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini a ɛyɛ ne deɛ no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔmfa ogyasɔ adeɛ nnyansramma ma mfiri afɔrebukyia no so, AWURADE anim, ne aduhwam a wɔasi no fekɔfekɔ ne nsa mmienu ma, na ɔmfa nkɔ ntwamutam no akyi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔmfa aduhwam no ngu ogya no so, AWURADE anim, na aduhwam no wisie nkata mpata adwa a ɛwɔ Adanseɛ no soɔ no ho, na wanwu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔmfa nantwinini no mogya no bi, na ɔmfa ne nsateaa nka mpete mpata adwa no so anim fam, na ɔmfa ne nsateaa nka mogya no bi mpete mpata adwa no anim hɔ mprɛ nson.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔnkum bɔne ho afɔdeɛ papo a ɔyɛ ɔman no deɛ no, na ɔmfa ne mogya nkɔ ntwamutam no akyi, na ɔmfa mogya no nyɛ sɛdeɛ ɔde nantwinini no mogya no yɛeɛ no, na ɔmfa mpete mpata adwa no so ne mpata adwa no anim,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na ɔmpata mma kronkronbea no, Israelfoɔ no afideɛ, ne wɔn mmara a wɔto, wɔn bɔne nyinaa nti; na saa na ɔnyɛ mma ahyiaeɛ ntomadan a ɛsi wɔn mu ɛsiane wɔn afideɛ no nti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na onipa biara nntena ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu, berɛ a ɔhyɛne hɔ kɔpata kronkronbea no mu, kɔsi sɛ ɔbɛfiri adie a wapata ama ɔno ara ne ne fie ne Israelfoɔ asafo nyinaa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔmfiri adi mmra afɔrebukyia a ɛsi AWURADE anim no ho, na ɔmpata mma no, na ɔmfa nantwinini no mogya no bi ne ɔpapo no mogya no bi nkeka afɔrebukyia no mmɛn ho nhyia,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na ɔmfa ne nsateaa nka mogya no bi mpete so mprɛ nson, na ɔnte ho nyɛ no kronkron mfiri Israelfoɔ no afideɛ mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na sɛ ɔpata ma kronkronbea ne ahyiaeɛ ntomadan ne afɔrebukyia no wie a, ɔmfa ɔpapo animono no mmra.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Aaron mfa ne nsa mmienu ngu ɔpapo animono no atifi, na ɔnka Israelfoɔ no mfomsoɔ nyinaa ne wɔn mmarato nyinaa sɛdeɛ wɔn bɔne teɛ no ɔmfa ngu ɔpapo no atifi, na ɔmma ɔbarima bi a ɔwɔ hɔ nkɔgyaa no mma no nkɔ ɛserɛ so,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na ɔpapo no nsoa wɔn mfomsoɔ nyinaa mfa nkɔ asase fo so.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Aaron nhyɛne ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu, na ɔnyi nwera atadeɛ a ɔhyɛ kɔɔ kronkronbea no, na ɔnnya no hɔ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔmfa nsuo nnware ne ho deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron, na ɔnhyɛ ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfiri adi nkɔbɔ ne hyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne ɔman no hyeɛ afɔdeɛ, na ɔmpata mma ɔno ara ne ho ne ɔman no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔnhye bɔne ho afɔdeɛ sradeɛ no afɔrebukyia no so.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na deɛ ɔde ɔpapo no kɔ kɔgyaa no maa Asasel no nsi ne ntadeɛ, na ɔmfa nsuo nnware ne ho, na ɛno akyi ansa na ɔmmra nsraban no mu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ papo a wɔde wɔn mogya kɔɔ kronkronbea hɔ kɔpataeɛ no, wɔmfa wɔn mfiri nkɔ nsraban no akyi, na wɔmfa ogya nhye wɔn nwoma ne wɔn nam ne wɔn agyanan.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na deɛ ɔkɔ kɔhyeeɛ no nsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware ne ho, na ɛno akyi ansa na waba nsraban no mu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na yei nyɛ mo daa ahyɛdeɛ: Bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no da a ɛtɔ so du no, mommrɛ mo ho ase, kuromani oo, ɔhɔhoɔ a ɔbɛsoɛ mo mu oo, monnyɛ adwuma biara.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na da no na wɔpata ma mo de dwira mo, na mo ho ate afiri mo bɔne nyinaa mu, AWURADE anim.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ɛnyɛ mo ɔhome mu homeda na mommrɛ mo ho ase: Ɛyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na mpata no, ɔsɔfoɔ a wɔasra no ngo a wɔde ahyɛ ne nsa sɛ ɔnni sɔfoɔ nsi n’agya ananmu no na ɔmpata, na ɔnhyɛ nwera ntadeɛ no, ntade kronkron no,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> na ɔmpata mma kronkronbea kronkron no, na ɔmpata mma ahyiaeɛ ntomadan ne afɔrebukyia no, na ɔmpata mma ɔsɔfoɔ no ne ɔman asafo mu no nyinaa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na yei nyɛ mo daa ahyɛdeɛ na wɔde apata ama Israelfoɔ afiri wɔn bɔne nyinaa mu prɛko daa afirinhyia. Na Mose yɛɛ sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ no no."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Aaron ne ne mma ne Israelfoɔ nyinaa, na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Yei ne asɛm a AWURADE ahyɛ ho mmara sɛ:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Obiara a ɔwɔ Israel fie a ɔkum nantwie anaa odwanten anaa abirekyie nsraban no mu anaasɛ ɔku no nsraban no akyire,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na ɔmfa mma ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano mmɛyɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ mma AWURADE wɔ tenabea anim no, wɔbɛbu mogya agu ne so, waka mogya agu, na wɔbɛtwa saa onipa no afiri ne man mu atwene,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na ama Israelfoɔ de wɔn afɔdeɛ a wɔkum wɔ ɛserɛ soɔ no abrɛ asɔfoɔ no ama wɔde abrɛ AWURADE wɔ ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na wɔakum abɔ AWURADE asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa mogya no mpete AWURADE afɔrebukyia no so, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, na ɔnhye sradeɛ no na ɛnyi hwa hwanhwam mma AWURADE.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔnnkum wɔn afɔrebɔdeɛ mmma mpapo abosom a wɔdi wɔn akyiri adwamammɔ soɔ no bio. Na ɛnyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ mma wɔn, wɔn awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Obiara a ɔfiri Israel fie anaa ahɔhoɔ a wɔabɛsoɛ wɔn mu no mu a ɔbɛbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ anaa okum afɔdeɛ bie,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na wamfa amma ahyiaeɛ ntomadan ano ammɛbɔ amma AWURADE no, wɔbɛtwa no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na obiara a ɔfiri Israel fie anaa ahɔhoɔ a wɔabɛsoɛ wɔn mu no mu a ɔdi mogya biara no, mɛma m’ani asa saa ɔkra a ɔdi mogya no, na matwa no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ ɔhonam biara nkwa wɔ mogya no mu, na mede ama mo, afɔrebukyia no so sɛ wɔmfa mpata mma mo ho; na mogya na wɔde pata ma ɔkra.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛno nti na mese Israelfoɔ sɛ: Mo mu biara nnni mogya, na ɔhɔhoɔ a wabɛsoɛ mo mu no nso nnni mogya.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na obiara a ɔfiri Israel mma ne ahɔhoɔ a wɔabɛsoɛ mo mu no a wɔyɛ ha kum aboa anaa anomaa a wɔdie no, wɔnhwie ne mogya ngu na wɔmfa dɔteɛ nkata so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔhonam nyinaa deɛ, ne mogya ne ne nkwa, enti na mese Israelfoɔ sɛ: Monnni nam biara mogya, ɛfiri sɛ honam nyinaa nkwa ne ne mogya; obiara a ɔdie no, wɔbɛtwa no atwene.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na obiara a ɔdi deɛ wawuo anaasɛ deɛ wɔatete no, kuromani oo, ɔhɔhoɔ oo, ɔnsi ne ntadeɛ na ɔmfa nsuo nnware, na ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ ansa na ne ho ate;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na sɛ wansi ne ntadeɛ na wannware ne ho a, ɛnneɛ ɔnsoa ne mmusuo."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Misraim asase a motenaa soɔ no so nneyɛɛ deɛ, monnyɛ. Na Kanaan asase a mede mo rekɔ soɔ no so nneyɛɛ nso, monnyɛ, na monnni wɔn ahyɛdeɛ so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> M’atemmudeɛ na monyɛ, na monkora m’ahyɛdeɛ sɛ mobɛdi soɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn. Na monkora m’ahyɛdeɛ ne m’atemmudeɛ a onipa a ɔyɛ no bɛnya mu nkwa no. Mene AWURADE.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Obiara nnkɔ ne bogya biara a ɔyɛ ne honam no ho nnkɔyi n’adagya so. Mene AWURADE.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nyi w’agya anaa wo na adagya so; wo na ne no, nyi n’adagya so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nyi w’agya yere adagya so; w’agya adagya ne no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wo nuabaa a ɔyɛ w’agya ba anaa wo na ba no, wɔwoo no efie oo, wɔwoo no baabi oo, nyi wɔn adagya so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wo babanin babaa anaa wo babaa babaa, nyi wɔn adagya so, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ w’adagya.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> W’agya yere babaa a w’agya awo no no, ɔyɛ wo nuabaa, nyi n’adagya so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nyi w’agya nuabaa adagya so; ɔyɛ w’agya honam.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nyi wo na nuabaa adagya so, ɛfiri sɛ ɔyɛ wo na honam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nyi w’agya nuabarima adagya so nkɔ ne yere ho; wo na kumaa ne no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nyi w’ase adagya so; wo babarima yere ne no, nyi n’adagya so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nyi wo nua yere adagya so; ɛyɛ wo nua adagya.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nyi ɔbaa bi ne ne ba adagya so; mfa ne babanin babaa anaa ne babaa babaa nyi wɔn adagya so; ne honam ne wɔn; ɛyɛ abusudeɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na mfa ɔbaa ne ne nua nware sɛ wobɛma wɔatwe kora, sɛ ɔda so te aseɛ no, wobɛyi n’adagya so aka ne ho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na nkɔ ɔbaa a ne nsabuo mu ne ho nteeɛ no ho nkɔyi n’adagya so.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wo ne wo yɔnko yere nnna, na mfa wo ho nsuo mma no mfa ngu wo ne no ho fi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mfa w’asefoɔ mu bi mmɔ afɔdeɛ mmma Molek, na ngu wo Nyankopɔn din ho fi; mene AWURADE.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wo ne ɔbarima nnna ɔbaa nna; ɛyɛ akyiwadeɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Wo ne aboa biara nnna mmfa nngu wo ho fi; na ɔbaa bi nnnyina aboa bi anim nnnane ne ho mmma no; ɛyɛ basabasayɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Mommfa nnoɔma yi biara nngu mo ho fi, ɛfiri sɛ yeinom nyinaa na amanaman a merebɛtu wɔn afiri mo anim yi de agu wɔn ho fi,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na asase no so agu fi, enti na meretua ɛso amumuyɛ no so ka, na asase no afe ɛsotefoɔ no agu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mo deɛ, monni m’ahyɛdeɛ ne m’atemmudeɛ so, na monnyɛ saa akyiwadeɛ yi mu biara, kuromani oo, ɔhɔhoɔ a wabɛsoɛ mo mu oo,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ɛfiri sɛ saa akyiwadeɛ yi nyinaa na asase no sofoɔ a wɔdi mo anim no ayɛ, na asase no so agu fi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na asase no amfe mo angu sɛ moagu ho fi, sɛdeɛ ɛfee amanaman a wɔdii mo anim no guiɛ no.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na obiara a ɔbɛyɛ saa akyiwadeɛ yi mu biara no, wɔbɛtwa wɔn a wɔyɛ no afiri wɔn man mu atwene.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Enti monhwɛ m’ahwɛdeɛ, na moanyɛ ahyɛdeɛ a wɔkyire a wɔdii mo anim yɛeɛ no amfa angu mo ho fi: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ asafo no nyinaa na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Monyɛ kronkron, ɛfiri sɛ me, AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, meyɛ kronkron.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Mo mu biara mmu ne na ne n’agya, na monni me home nna no: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Monnnane mo ho nnkɔ abosonhuhuo no nkyɛn, na monnyɛ ahoni a wɔaguo te sɛ anyame mmfa: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ mobɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ma AWURADE a, mommɔ no sɛdeɛ ɛbɛma moasɔ ani:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Da a mokum no ara na wɔnnie, ne n’adekyeeɛ, na deɛ ɛbɛka akɔduru nnansa no, wɔmfa ogya nhye.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ wɔdi no da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no a, ɛyɛ akyiwadeɛ, ɛnsɔ ani;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na deɛ ɔdie no bɛsoa ne mmusuo, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE akronkronneɛ na wagu ho fi, na wɔbɛtwa saa ɔkra no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ motwa mo asase so nnɔbaeɛ a, nwie wo nkwanseɛ deɛ no twa, na nni w’afuomdeɛ no mu mpɛpɛ;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na wo bobe turo nso, nni mu mpɛpɛ, na wo turo mu aba a ɛgugu fam no, ntase; gya ma ohiani ne ɔhɔhoɔ: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mommmɔ korɔno, na monnni kusum, na obiara nntwa ne yɔnko nkontompo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na monnka me din ho ntam atorɔ mu, na woanhura wo Nyankopɔn din ho: Mene AWURADE.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nni wo yɔnko amim na ntwa no dwo. Mma wo paani akatua nnka wo nkyɛn mma adeɛ nnkye.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nnome ɔsotifoɔ na mfa suntidua nto onifirani anim, na suro Onyankopɔn: Mene AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Monntwa atemmuo mu nkontompo. Nhwɛ mmɔborɔni anim, na nyɛ deɛ ɛbɛsɔ otumfoɔ ani; tenenee mu na bu wo yɔnko atɛn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nkyini wo nkurɔfoɔ mu nni nsekuro; nsɔre ntia wo yɔnko mogya. Mene AWURADE.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ntane wo nua w’akoma mu; ka na ka wo yɔnko anim, na woansoa ne ho bɔne.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ntɔ were na nnya wo nkurɔfoɔ mu biara ho menasepɔ, na dɔ wo yɔnko sɛ wo ho: Mene AWURADE.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Monni m’ahyɛdeɛ so. Mma w’afieboa nnni afrafra mmforo wɔn ho; w’afuo nso, mfa adeɛ mfrafra nnua mu, na mma ntoma ahodoɔ mmienu nsasaawa nnka wo ho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sɛ ɔbarima bi ne ɔbaa da na ɔde ne ho ka no, na ɔbaa no yɛ afenaa a wɔde no ama obi awareɛ, na gyeɛ na wɔnnya nnyee no anaasɛ wɔnnya mfaa ne ho nkyɛɛ no a, wɔmpeepee mu ntwe wɔn aso, na wɔnnku wɔn, ɛfiri sɛ ɔnne ne ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔbarima no mfa n’asodie ho afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no ano, asodie ho afɔdeɛ dwennini na ɔmfa mmra.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa asodie ho afɔdeɛ dwennini no mpata mma no, AWURADE anim, bɔne a wayɛ no nti, na wɔde ne bɔne a wayɛ no akyɛ no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na sɛ moduru asase no so na motɛ dua biara a wɔdie a, mommu n’aba no sɛ momonotodeɛ; mfeɛ mmiɛnsa na ɛnyɛ mo momonotodeɛ, wɔnnni;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na afe a ɛtɔ so nnan no, ɛso aba nyinaa nyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE ayeyie;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na afe a ɛtɔ so nnum no, monni n’aba, na ne nnɔbaeɛ nkɔ so nnɔɔso mma mo: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mommfa mogya nnka biribi ho nnni. Monnni adebisasɛm na monngoro abayigorɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Monnkonton mo nwi ano, na nsɛe wo bɔgyesɛ ano.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Mommotabota mo ho mmma awufoɔ, na monnkurukyire mo ho atwerɛ biara: Mene AWURADE.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nhura wo babaa ho mma no mmmɔ adwaman, na asase no ammɔ adwaman, na mmusuo anyɛ asase no so ma.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Monni me home nna na monsuro me kronkronbea no: Mene AWURADE.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Monnnane mo ho nnkɔ ɔdebisafoɔ nkyɛn, na monnhwehwɛ adunsinfoɔ akyiri kwan mmfa nngu mo ho fi wɔ wɔn ho: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Fa obuo ma ɔpanin, aane di akɔkoraa ni, na suro wo Nyankopɔn: Mene AWURADE.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na sɛ ɔhɔhoɔ bi bɛsoɛ mo asase so a, monnhyɛ ne so.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ɔhɔhoɔ a wabɛtena mo mu nyɛ mo sɛ mo kuromani bi, na dɔ no sɛ wo ho, ɛfiri sɛ moyɛɛ Misraim asase so ahɔhoɔ: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Monntwa atemmuo mu nkontompo, adesusuo, adekarie ne adehyɛ mu;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> nsania tee, abrammoɔ tee, efa tee ne susutoa tee na monkura: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn a meyii mo firii Misraim asase soɔ no.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na monni m’ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa ne m’atemmudeɛ nyinaa so nyɛ: Mene AWURADE."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ka kyerɛ Israelfoɔ no sɛ: Obiara a ɔfiri Israelfoɔ anaa ahɔhoɔ a wɔabɛtena Israel mu no mu a ɔde ne mma mu bi ma Molek no, kum na wɔnku no; asase no sofoɔ nsi no aboɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na me nso mɛma m’ani asa onipa no, na matwa no afiri ne man mu atwene, ɛfiri sɛ, ɔde ne mma mu bi ama Molek de agu me kronkronbea no ho fi na wahura me din kronkron no ho.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na sɛ ɔde ne mma mu bi ma Molek na asase no sofoɔ no bu wɔn ani gu saa onipa no so na wɔanku no a,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> me deɛ, mɛma m’ani asa onipa no ne n’abusua, na mɛtwa ɔno ne wɔn a wɔdi n’akyire adwamammɔ kwan soɔ na wɔdi Molek akyire bɔ adwaman no nyinaa afiri wɔn man mu agu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na obiara a ɔdane ne ho kɔ adebisafoɔ anaa adunsinfoɔ nkyɛn kɔdi wɔn akyi adwamammɔ kwan soɔ no, mɛma m’ani asa saa onipa no, na mɛtwa no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Enti monte mo ho na monyɛ kronkron, na mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na monni m’ahyɛdeɛ so na monyɛ: Mene AWURADE a ɔyɛ mo kronkron no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ obiara dome n’agya anaa ne na a, kum na wɔnku no; wadome n’agya ne ne na, ne mogya gu n’atifi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɔbarima a ɔfa ɔbarima bi yere na ɔne ne yɔnko yere sɛe awadeɛ no, kum na wɔnkum ɔbarima ne ɔbaa awaresɛefoɔ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔne n’agya yere da no, wayi n’agya adagya so; kum na wɔnkum wɔn baanu nyinaa; wɔn mogya gu wɔn atifi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔne n’ase a ɔyɛ ne ba yere da no, kum na wɔnkum wɔn baanu nyinaa; wɔayɛ akyiwadeɛ. Wɔn mogya gu wɔn atifi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔne ɔbarima bi da ɔbaa nna no, wɔn baanu ayɛ akyiwadeɛ, kum na wɔnku wɔn; wɔn mogya gu wɔn atifi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sɛ ɔbarima bi fa ɔbaa ne ne na nyinaa a, ɛyɛ abusudeɛ. Wɔmfa ogya nhye ɔno ne wɔn nyinaa, na abusudeɛ antena mo mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔne aboa bi da no, kum na wɔnku no, na aboa no nso monku no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔbaa a ɔkɔ aboa biara ho kɔda hɔ ma no no, kum ɔbaa no ne aboa no; kum na wɔnku wɔn; wɔn mogya gu wɔn atifi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔfa ne nuabaa a ɔyɛ n’agya ba anaa ne na ba na ɔhunu n’adagya na ɔbaa no nso hunu n’adagya no, ɛyɛ animguasedeɛ, na wɔntwitwa wɔn ngu, wɔn man mma anim; wayi ne nuabaa adagya so; ɔnsoa ne mmusuo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔne ɔbaa a wabu ne nsa da na ɔyi n’adagya soɔ na ɔbue n’abura ano, na ɔno nso yi ne mogya abura soɔ no, wɔntwitwa wɔn baanu nyinaa mfiri wɔn man mu ngu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na nyi wo na nuabaa anaa w’agya nuabaa adagya so, ɛfiri sɛ wayi ne bogya adagya so; wɔnsoa wɔn mmusuo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔbarima a ɔne n’agya nua yere da, wayi n’agya nua adagya so, wɔnsoa wɔn bɔne, wɔrenwo mma na wɔawu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na obi fa ne nua yere ware a, ɛyɛ adeɛ a ɛho nteɛ; wayi ne nua adagya so, wɔrennya ɔba.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Enti monni m’ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa ne m’atemmudeɛ nyinaa so na monyɛ, na asase a mede mo rekɔ akɔtena soɔ no amfe mo angu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na mommfa aman a merebɛtu wɔn mo anim ho ahyɛdeɛ so; na wɔayɛ yeinom nyinaa na wɔn ho ayɛ me nwunu;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na mese mo sɛ: Mo na monni wɔn asase soɔ, na mede mema mo sɛ momfa, asase a nufosuo ne ɛwoɔ sene wɔ soɔ. Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn a mayi mo afiri amanaman mu no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mompae asase so mmoa a wɔn ho teɛ ne wɔn a wɔn ho nteɛ mu, ne nnomaa a wɔn ho nteɛ ne wɔn a wɔn ho teɛ mu, na moamfa asase so mmoa ne nnomaa ne adeɛ biara a ɛwea fam a mapae mu mama mo sɛ ɛho nteɛ no angu mo kra ho fi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na monyɛ kronkron mma me, ɛfiri sɛ me AWURADE, meyɛ kronkron. Na mayi mo afiri aman mu sɛ mommɛyɛ me deɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔbarima anaa ɔbaa a adebisa anaa akɔm honhom wɔ ne mu no, kum na wɔnku wɔn; wɔnsi wɔn aboɔ; wɔn mogya gu wɔn atifi."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ: Kasa kyerɛ Aaron mma asɔfoɔ no na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo mu biara nngu ne ho fi efunu bi ho ne man mu,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> gye ne bogya a ɔbɛn no, ne na ne n’agya ne ne babanin ne ne babaa ne ne nuabarima,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ne ne nuabaa a ɔyɛ ɔbaabunu a ɔbɛn no a ɔnnya nnyaa kunu, ɔno ho na ɔmma ne ho nkum.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɔyɛ ne nkurɔfoɔ mu nipa titire nti, ɔnngu ne ho fi, nanso ɔnnhura ne ho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wɔnnyi wɔn mpampam na wɔnnwɛre wɔn bɔgyesɛ ano, na wɔmmmotabota wɔn honam mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wɔnyɛ kronkron mma wɔn Nyankopɔn, na wɔnnhura wɔn Nyankopɔn din ho, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn na wɔde AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ, wɔn Nyankopɔn aduane no ba; enti wɔnyɛ kronkron.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wɔnnware ɔbaa dwamamfoɔ bi anaa deɛ ne ho ahura, nanso wɔnnware ɔbaa a ne kunu ako no, ɛfiri sɛ ɔyɛ kronkron ma ne Nyankopɔn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na bu no kronkron, ɛfiri sɛ wo Nyankopɔn aduane na ɔde ba; ɔnyɛ onipa kronkron mma wo, ɛfiri sɛ kronkron ne me AWURADE a ɔyɛ mo kronkron no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ babaa firi aseɛ bɔ adwaman a, wahura n’agya ho, wɔmfa ogya nhye no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ne nuanom mu sɔfo panin a wɔahwie sra ngo agu n’atifi na wɔde ahyɛ ne nsam sɛ ɔnhyɛ ntadeɛ no, ɔmmpɛsɛ ne ti na ɔnnsunsuane ne ntadeɛ mu,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɔnnkɔ efunu biara ho, n’agya ne ne na ho mpo ɔmmma ne ho nnkum.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔmmfiri kronkronbea hɔ, na ɔnnhura ne Nyankopɔn kronkronbea ho, ɛfiri sɛ ne Nyankopɔn sra ngo no wɔ n’atifi: Mene AWURADE.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔno deɛ, ɔbaabunu na ɔnwareɛ;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> okunafoɔ ne deɛ wɔako no ne deɛ ne ho ahura ne odwamamfoɔ deɛ, ɔnnware yeinom mu biara, na mmom ne man mu baabunu na ɔnwareɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔnnhura n’asefoɔ ho ne man mu: Na mene AWURADE a meyɛ no kronkron.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Aaron sɛ: W’asefoɔ awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ mu barima a ɔdi dɛm biara mmma mmmɛfa ne Nyankopɔn aduane no mmma;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na obiara a ɔdi dɛm no mmmɛn, onifirani oo, apakye oo, hwento oo, deɛ ne honam biribi boro so oo,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> deɛ ne nan anaa ne nsa abu oo,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> afu oo, epira oo, deɛ ɛtɛ si n’ani soɔ oo, deɛ ɔyare ntwom oo, ogyatɔni oo, deɛ ne hwewa nnwoa abobɔ oo,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɔsɔfoɔ Aaron asefoɔ mu biara a ɔdi dɛm no nntwe mmpini mmmɛfa AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ no mma; ɛdɛm wɔ ne ho, ɔmmfa ne Nyankopɔn aduane no nntwe mmpini.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ne Nyankopɔn aduane, akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron ɛne akronkronneɛ no deɛ, ɔnni bi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ntwamutam no ho nko na ɔmmma, na afɔrebukyia no ho na ɔnntwe mmpini, ɛfiri sɛ ɛdɛm wɔ ne ho: Na wanhura m’akronkronneɛ no ho, ɛfiri sɛ mene AWURADE a meyɛ wɔn kronkron.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Mose ka kyerɛɛ Aaron ne ne mma ne Israelfoɔ nyinaa."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Aaron ne ne mma sɛ wɔnte wɔn ho mfiri Israelfoɔ akronkronneɛ ho, na wɔnnhura me din kronkron no ho, adeɛ a wɔyɛ no kronkron ma me no mu: Mene AWURADE.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ mu barima biara a ɔfiri mo asefoɔ nyinaa mu a ɔba akronkronneɛ a Israelfoɔ ayɛ no kronkron ama AWURADE na ne fi wɔ ne soɔ no, wɔbɛtwa saa ɔkra no afiri m’anim atwene: Mene AWURADE.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Aaron asefoɔ mu barima biara a ɔyɛ ɔkwatani anaa deɛ ne ho sene no nnni akronkronneɛ no bi kɔsi sɛ ne ho bɛteɛ; na deɛ ɔka adeɛ a efunu agu ɛho fi anaa obi a ne ho nsuo afiri ne mu,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> anaa obi a ɔka adeɛ biara a ɛwea a ɛmma ne ho nteɛ anaa ɔka onipa biara a ne ho wɔ fi no, ho nte;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ɔkra a ɔka no, ne ho nte kɔsi anwummerɛ, na ɔnnni akronkronneɛ no bi gye sɛ ɔde nsuo adware ne ho ansa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ owia kɔtɔ a, ne ho te, ɛno akyiri ansa na ɔnni akronkronneɛ no bie, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ n’aduane.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Aboa funu anaa deɛ wɔatete ne mu no, ɔnnni mmfa nngu ne ho fi: Mene AWURADE.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔnhwɛ m’ahwɛdeɛ na wɔansoa ɛho bɔne, na sɛ wɔhura ho a, wɔanwuwu: Mene AWURADE a meyɛ wɔn kronkron no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɔhɔhoɔ biara nnni akronkronneɛ no bi, na deɛ wabɛtena ɔsɔfoɔ bi nkyɛn anaa ɔpaani nnni akronkronneɛ no bi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ bi de ne sika tɔ onipa bi a, ɔno deɛ, ɔnni bi, ɛne deɛ wɔwoo no ne fie, wɔn na wɔnni n’aduane no bie.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ babaa bi kɔware ɔhɔhoɔ bi a, ɔnnni akronkronneɛ mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ no bi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ ɔsɔfoɔ babaa yi yɛ okunafoɔ anaasɛ wɔako no, na ɔnni ba, na ɔsane ba n’agya fie sɛ ne mmɔfraase a, ɔnni n’agya aduane no bi; na ɔhɔhoɔ biara deɛ, ɔnnni bi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ obi anhyɛda, na ɔdi akronkronneɛ no bi a, ɔmfa n’abupɛn nnum mu baako mpae so, na ɔnnane akronkronneɛ no mma ɔsɔfoɔ no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔnnhura Israelfoɔ no akronkronneɛ a wɔde bɔ afɔdeɛ ma AWURADE no ho,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na wɔmmma wɔnnsoa asodie bɔne bi wɔn akronkronneɛ no die mu, ɛfiri sɛ mene AWURADE a ɔyɛ wɔn kronkron.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Aaron ne ne mma ne Israelfoɔ no nyinaa na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Obiara a ɔfiri Israel fie anaa Israel mu ahɔhoɔ mu a ɔde n’ayɛyɛdeɛ bɛba, wɔn bɔhyɛ adeɛ biara anaa wɔn ayamyi adeɛ biara a wɔde brɛ AWURADE abɛbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ɛbɛsɔ ani ama mo nti, ɛnyɛ onini a ɔdi mu a ɔfiri anantwie, nnwanten anaa mmirekyie mu;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> adeɛ biara a ɛdɛm wɔ ne ho no, mommfa mmma, ɛfiri sɛ ɛrensɔ ani mma mo.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na obiara a ɔde asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ bɛbrɛ AWURADE sɛ ɔde rewie n’aboadeɛ ma anaa ayamyi adeɛ a ɛfiri anantwie anaa nnwan mu no, ɔmma no nni mu, na ɛnsɔ ani; ɛnnni dɛm biara.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Deɛ n’ani afira anaasɛ wabubuo anaasɛ wapira anaasɛ watutu akuro anaasɛ ntwom anaa nsoa agu ne ho no, mommfa yeinom biara mmmrɛ AWURADE, na mommfa wɔn mu biara nnsɔ afɔrebukyia no so gya mmma AWURADE.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na nantwie anaa odwan a ne ho biribi boro soɔ anaasɛ watɔ ape no, ayamyi afɔdeɛ deɛ, fa no bɔ, na aboadeɛ deɛ, ɛnsɔ ani.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na deɛ wɔapɛkyɛ, wɔabɔ, wɔatu anaa wɔasa no no, mommfa mmmrɛ AWURADE, na mo asase so nso monnyɛ saa.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔnanani bi nsam nso monnnye yeinom mu biara mmfa mmmɛyɛ mo Nyankopɔn aduane, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn ho aka, ɛdɛm wɔ wɔn ho, ɛrensɔ ani mma mo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nantwie, odwanten anaa abirekyie, sɛ wɔwo no a, ɔntena ne na ase nnanson, na ɛfiri da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe de rekorɔ no, wɔde yɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ ma AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ a ɛbɛsɔ ani.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na monnkum nantwie anaa odwan ne ne ba nyinaa da koro.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na sɛ mobɔ aseda afɔdeɛ ma AWURADE a, mommɔ no sɛdeɛ ɛbɛma moasɔ ani;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> da no ara wɔnni; monnnya mu bi nnkɔsi anɔpa: Mene AWURADE.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na monni me mmara nsɛm so na monyɛ: Mene AWURADE.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na monnhura me din kronkron no ho, na wɔmmu me kronkron Israelfoɔ mu: Mene AWURADE a meyɛ mo kronkron a",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> meyii mo firii Misraim asase soɔ sɛ merebɛyɛ mo Nyankopɔn: Mene AWURADE."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: AWURADE afahyɛ ahodoɔ a mompae sɛ ɛnyɛ nhyia kronkron, m’afahyɛ nna no nie.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nnansia na wɔnyɛ adwuma, na da a ɛtɔ so nson no yɛ home mu homeda, wɔnhyia nhyia kronkron; monnyɛ adwuma biara, ɛyɛ AWURADE homeda mo tenabea nyinaa mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Yeinom ne AWURADE afahyɛ, nhyia kronkron a mompae ne mmerɛ mu no:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bosome a ɛdi kan no da a ɛtɔ so dunan no anwummerɛ yɛ AWURADE twam;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na bosome no ara da a ɛtɔ so dunum no yɛ AWURADE apiti afahyɛ, nnanson na monni apiti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Da a ɛdi kan no monhyia nhyia kronkron; monnyɛ adwumaden biara.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na momfa ogya afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE nnanson; da a ɛtɔ so nson no monhyia nhyia kronkron; monnyɛ adwumaden biara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ moduru asase a mede merema mo no so na motwa ɛso nnɔbaeɛ a, momfa mo nnɔbaeɛ fi a ɛdi kan no mmrɛ ɔsɔfoɔ;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɔnhim efi no AWURADE anim, na ɛnsɔ ani mma mo; homeda no, adeɛ kye a, na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhim.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛda a mohim efi no, momfa odwanten ba a ɔdi mu a wadi afe mmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ mma AWURADE,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ne ɛho aduane afɔdeɛ, esiam abupɛn du mu mmienu a wɔde ngo afɔre, na ɛnyɛ AWURADE ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ne ɛho ahwiesa, bobesa susutoa abupɛn nnan mu baako.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na monnni paanoo anaa ayuo a wɔato anaasɛ wɔasie kɔsi da no ara a mode mo Nyankopɔn ayɛyɛdeɛ reba no. Ɛnyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ mma mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ, mo tenabea nyinaa mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na monkan nna mfa mfiri homeda no akyiri da, da a mode ohim fi no ba no ɛnyɛ nnawɔtwe nson pɛpɛɛpɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Monkan adaduonum nkɔsi homeda a ɛtɔ so nson no akyiri da so ansa na mode aduane afɔdeɛ foforɔ abrɛ AWURADE.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Momfa ohim paanoo mmienu mfiri mo tenabea mmra; esiam abupɛn du mu mmienu mmɔreka na wɔmfa nto, na ɛnyɛ aduanekan mma AWURADE.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na momfa nnwanten mma nson a wɔdi mu a wɔadi afe afe ne nantwiburuwa baako ne adwennini mmienu nka paanoo no ho; wɔnyɛ AWURADE ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne ɛho aduane afɔdeɛ ne ahwiesa, ogya afɔdeɛ a ɛyi hwa hwanhwam ma AWURADE.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na momfa ɔpapo baako mmɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne nnwanten mma mmienu a wɔadi afe afe mmɔ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no nhim wɔn ne aduanekan paanoo no ne nnwanten mma mmienu no na ɛnyɛ AWURADE anim ohim afɔdeɛ: Ɛnyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE na wɔmfa mma ɔsɔfoɔ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na monhyia da no ara; ɛnyɛ mo nhyia kronkron, monnyɛ adwuma den biara. Ɛnyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ mo tenabea nyinaa mu, mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na sɛ motwa mo asase so nnɔbaeɛ a, nwie w’afuo nkwanseɛ deɛ twa, na nni wo nnɔbaeɛ no mu mpɛpɛ: Gya ma ohiani ne ɔhɔhoɔ: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ: Bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no da a ɛdi kan nyɛ mo homeda, totorobɛntohyɛn nkaeɛ, nhyia kronkron;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> monnyɛ adwumaden biara, na momfa ogya afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bosome a ɛtɔ so nson yi ara da a ɛtɔ so du ne mpata da; monhyia nhyia kronkron, na mommrɛ mo ho ase na momfa ogya afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɛda no monnyɛ adwuma biara, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ mpata da a wɔpata ma mo, AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na obiara a ɔmmrɛ ne ho ase da no no, wɔbɛtwa no afiri ne man mu atwene.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na onipa biara a ɔyɛ adwuma bi saa da no no, mɛsɛe saa onii ko no afiri ne man mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Monnyɛ adwuma biara; ɛyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ ma mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ, mo tenabea nyinaa mu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛyɛ home mu homeda ma mo, na mommrɛ mo ho ase bosome no da a ɛtɔ so nkron no anwummerɛ; monni mo homeda no mfiri anwummerɛ nkɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ sɛ: Bosome a ɛtɔ so nson yi da a ɛtɔ so dunum no yɛ asese afahyɛ nnanson ma AWURADE.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Da a ɛdi kan no yɛ nhyia kronkron; monnyɛ adwumaden biara.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Nnanson na momfa ogya afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE; da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no nyɛ mo nhyia kronkron, na momfa ogya afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE; ɛyɛ afahyɛ awieeɛ, monnyɛ adwumaden biara.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Yeinom ne AWURADE afahyɛ ahodoɔ a mompae sɛ wɔnhyia nhyia kronkron no, na wɔmfa ogya afɔdeɛ mmrɛ AWURADE, ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aduane afɔdeɛ ne kum afɔdeɛ ne ahwiesa, ebiara wɔ ne da mu.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ɛsono AWURADE home nna no, na ɛsono mo ayɛyɛdeɛ, na ɛsono mo aboadeɛ nyinaa, na ɛsono mo ayamyi adeɛ nyinaa a mode ma AWURADE no.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Nso bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no da a ɛtɔ so dunum a moreboa asase so nnɔbaeɛ ano no, monni AWURADE nnapɔnna nnanson: Da a ɛdi kan no yɛ homeda, na ɛda a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no yɛ homeda.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na ɛda a ɛdi kan no, momfa nnua afɛfɛ so adeɛ, ɛberɛ ne nnua kusuu mman ne nsunoa nnua, na mo ani nnye AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn anim nnanson.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na momfa nni nnapɔnna mma AWURADE, nnanson daa afe. Ɛyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ ma mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ; bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no mu na monni nnapɔnna yi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Asese mu na montena nnanson, Israel man mma nyinaa ntena asese mu,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> na mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ ahunu sɛ meyii Israelfoɔ firii Misraim asase soɔ no, asese mu na memaa wɔtenaeɛ: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na Mose paee AWURADE afahyɛ no kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hyɛ Israelfoɔ ma wɔmmrɛ wo ngodua aba a wɔasie ngo korɔgyenn na wɔmfa nsɔ kanea no, na kanea no nsi so daa;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> adanseɛ ntwamutam no akyi, ahyiaeɛ ntomadan no mu na Aaron nsiesie mfiri anwummerɛ nkɔsi anɔpa, AWURADE anim daa; ɛyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ ma mo awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sika amapa kaneadua a ɛho teɛ no so na ɔnsiesie nkanea no, AWURADE anim daa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na fa esiam to taterɛ dummienu; olonka abupɛn du mu mmienu nyɛ taterɛ baako.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na fa sesɛ so akyerɛpɛn mmienu, nsia nyɛ kyerɛpɛn baako, ɛpono a ɛho teɛ no so, AWURADE anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na fa ohwamfufuo korɔgyenn toto akyerɛpɛn no so, na ɛnyɛ paanoo no so nkaeɛ adeɛ, ogya afɔdeɛ a wɔsɔ ma AWURADE.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Daa homeda na ɔnsiesie wɔ AWURADE anim daa, ɛyɛ Israelfoɔ fam daa apam;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɛnyɛ Aaron ne ne mma deɛ, na wɔnni wɔ deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron a ɛfiri AWURADE gya afɔdeɛ so ma no, ɛyɛ daa kyɛfa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Israelni baa bi ba a n’agya yɛ Misraimni firii adi Israelfoɔ no mu, na Israelni baa no ba no ne Israelni bi hamee nsraban no mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Israelni baa no ba no kaa edin no ho abususɛm, na ɔdomee. Na wɔde no brɛɛ Mose. Nso ne na din de Selomit, Dibri ba a ɔfiri Dan abusuakuo mu;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wɔbɔɔ no dua mu sɛ ɛnkɔsi sɛ ɔbɛnya AWURADE anomu asɛm aka akyerɛ wɔn.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Fa deɛ wadome no firi adi kɔ nsraban no akyi, na wɔn a wɔteeɛ no nyinaa mfa wɔn nsa ngu n’atifi, na asafo no nyinaa nsi no aboɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ nso sɛ: Obiara a ɔbɛdome ne Nyankopɔn no, ɔbɛsoa ne bɔne.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na deɛ ɔka AWURADE din ho abususɛm no, kum na wɔnku no: Sie na asafo no nyinaa nsi no aboɔ; ɔhɔhoɔ oo, kuromani oo, sɛ ɔka edin no ho abususɛm a, wɔnku no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na sɛ obi kum onipa biara a, kum na wɔnku no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na deɛ ɔkum afieboa no, ɔnsi ananmu, ɔkra nsi ɔkra ananmu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na deɛ ɔpira ne yɔnko nipa no, sɛdeɛ ɔyɛeɛ no, wɔnyɛ no saa ara:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ebuo nsi ebuo ananmu, ani nsi ani ananmu, ɛse nsi ɛse ananmu; sɛdeɛ ɔpiraa onipa no, saa ara na wɔnyɛ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na deɛ ɔkum afieboa no, ɔnsi ananmu, na deɛ ɔkum onipa no, wɔnku no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Atemmuo koro nna hɔ mma mo, ɔhɔhoɔ nyɛ sɛ okuromani. Na mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na Mose kasa kyerɛɛ Israelfoɔ, na wɔde deɛ ɔdomeeɛ no firii adi kɔɔ nsraban no akyi kɔsii no aboɔ. Na Israelfoɔ yɛɛ sɛdeɛ AWURADE hyɛɛ Mose no."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose Sinai bepɔ so sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ moduru asase a mede merema mo no so a, asase no nhome nni home afe mma AWURADE.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Mfeɛ nsia na dua w’afuo mu adeɛ, na mfeɛ nsia no pempane wo bobe turo mu nnua ho na boa emu nnɔbaeɛ ano;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na afe a ɛtɔ so nson no nyɛ ahomegyeɛ home mma asase no, ɛnyɛ home mma AWURADE: Nnua w’afuo mu adeɛ, na mpempane wo bobe turo mu nnua ho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wo ntwakaeɛ a ɛfifire no, ntwa, na wo bobehoma a woampempane no so esa esa no, ntete, ɛnyɛ ahomegyeɛ afe mma asase no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na asase no home mu adeɛ nyɛ mo deɛ, na monni, wo ne w’akoa ne w’afenaa ne wo paani ne wo hɔhoɔ a wɔabɛtena wo nkyɛn,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ne w’afieboa ne mmoa a wɔwɔ w’asase no soɔ, na ɛso nnɔbaeɛ no nyinaa nyɛ wɔn aduane.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na kan home mfeɛ nson, mfeɛ nson ahodoɔ nson, fa, na home mfeɛ nson no mu nna nyɛ aduanan nkron.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na bosome a ɛtɔ so nson no da a ɛtɔ so du no, ma wɔnhyɛne totorobɛnto ntwa mu; mpata da no mu na momma wɔnhyɛne totorobɛnto ntwam mo asase nyinaa soɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na monyɛ afe a ɛtɔ so aduonum no afe kronkron, na mompae ahofadie, asase no so, mma ɛsotefoɔ nyinaa; ɛnyɛ mo ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ na mo mu biara nsane nkɔ mo agyapadeɛ mu, na obiara nsane nkɔ n’abusua mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ na saa afe a ɛtɔ so aduonum no nyɛ mma mo: Monnnua adeɛ na monntwa ne ntwakaeɛ a ɛfifiriiɛ, na monntete mo bobe homa a wɔampempane ho no so aba.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛyɛ ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe, ɛnyɛ kronkron mma mo. Monni mfuo mu nnɔbaeɛ a ɛba afe no mu no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe yi mu no, mo mu biara nsane nkɔ mo agyapadeɛ mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ wotɔn biribi ma wo yɔnko anaasɛ wotɔ wo yɔnko nsam biribi a, mo mu bi nnni ne nua amim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛdeɛ ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no akyiri mfirinhyia ano teɛ na tɔ wo yɔnko nkyɛn adeɛ, sɛdeɛ nnɔbaeɛ mfirinhyia ano teɛ na ɔntɔn mma woɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mfeɛ no dɔɔso a, to ne boɔ so, na mfeɛ no sua a, te ne boɔ so, ɛfiri sɛ afe afe nnɔbaeɛ na ɔtɔn ma woɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mo mu biara nnni ne yɔnko amim, na suro wo Nyankopɔn: Na mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na monyɛ m’ahyɛdeɛ na monni m’atemmudeɛ so nyɛ, na montena asase no so dwoodwoo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na asase no bɛba n’aduane na moadi amee, na moatena so dwoodwoo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na sɛ moka sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na yɛbɛdi afe a ɛtɔ so nson no mu? Hwɛ, yɛnnua na yɛntwa yɛn nnɔbaeɛ a,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ɛnneɛ, mɛhyɛ me nhyira mama mo afe a ɛtɔ so nsia no mu, na aba mfeɛ mmiɛnsa aduane;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na modua aduane afe a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe no mu a, mobɛdi nnɔbaeɛ dada no akɔsi afe a ɛtɔ so nkron no mu. Mobɛdi aduane dada no akɔsi sɛ ne nnɔbaeɛ bɛba.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔnntɔn asase no korakora, ɛfiri sɛ asase no yɛ me dea na moyɛ me nkyɛn ahɔhoɔ ne atubrafoɔ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na asase a modi soɔ nyinaa, momma asase no gyeɛ ho kwan.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sɛ ɛhia wo nua na ɔtɔn n’adeɛ bi a, ɛnneɛ ne gyefoɔ a ɔyɛ obusuani a ɔbɛn no mmra mmɛgye deɛ ne nua tɔneeɛ no.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na sɛ obi nni gyefoɔ na ne nsa aso na wanya deɛ ɛso gyeɛ a,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ɛnneɛ, ɔmmu mfeɛ a ɔtɔneeɛ no ano na ɔnhyɛ deɛ ɛboro soɔ no ananmu mma deɛ ɔtɔn maa no no, na ɔnsane mmra n’adeɛ ho.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na sɛ ne nsa anso deɛ ɛso ananmuhyɛ no so a, ɛnneɛ, adeɛ a ɔtɔneeɛ no ntena deɛ ɔtɔeɛ no nsam nkɔsi ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no, na ɛfiri ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no mu no, ɔnsane mmra n’adeɛ ho.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na sɛ obi tɔn efie a wɔtena mu wɔ kuro a ɔfasuo wɔ ho mu a, wɔmma ne gyeɛ ho kwan nkɔsi sɛ ne tɔn afe no duru soɔ; nna yi na ɔwɔ ne gyeɛ ho kwan.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na sɛ wannye ma afe mu wie duru a, ɛnneɛ, efie a ɛwɔ kuro a ɔfasuo wɔ ho mu no nyɛ deɛ ɔtɔeɛ no dea korakora, n’awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu; ɔdenadeɛ no ntumi mmɛgye bio ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na adan a ɛwowɔ nkuraa a ɔfasuo nni ho aseɛ no deɛ, wɔmmu nka asase no so mfuo ho: Wɔmma ne gyeɛ ho kwan; na wɔmmɛgye no ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no mu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Lewifoɔ nkuro a ɛyɛ nkuro a wɔdi soɔ no mu afie deɛ, Lewifoɔ wɔ ne gyeɛ ho kwan daa.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na sɛ Lewifoɔ mu bi annye ne fie a wɔatɔn a ɛwɔ kuro a ɔdi soɔ mu a, ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no mu no, ɔmfa n’adeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ Lewifoɔ nkuro mu afie ne wɔn adeɛ a wɔdi soɔ Israelfoɔ mu.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na wɔn nkuro ho mmoa adidibea nsase deɛ, wɔnntɔn, na ɛyɛ wɔn adeɛ a wɔdi so daa.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na sɛ ɛhia wo nua na ɔpa aba a, sɔ ne mu na ɔntena wo nkyɛn sɛ ɔhɔhoɔ ne otudanfoɔ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Nnye ne hɔ mfɛntomu, na nhuri ne ka a ɔde woɔ no, na suro wo Nyankopɔn, na wo nua nnya wo nkyɛn nkwa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Mfa wo sika mma no nnye ɛho mfɛntomu, na nhuri w’aduane a woma no no:",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn a meyii mo firii Misraim asase soɔ sɛ mede Kanaan asase merema mo na mayɛ mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na sɛ ɛhia wo nua a ɔwɔ wo nkyɛn na wɔtɔn no ma wo a, nni no nya,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> na mmom ɔntena wo nkyɛn sɛ ɔpaani ne otudanfoɔ; ɔnsom wo nkɔsi ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no so.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ɛno na ɔmfiri wo nkyɛn, ɔno ne ne mma nyinaa, na ɔnsane nkɔ n’abusua mu ne n’agyanom adeɛ a wɔdi soɔ no ho.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na wɔyɛ me nkoa a meyii wɔn firii Misraim asase so. Wɔnntɔn wɔn nkoatɔn.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Mfa nyadie nhyɛ no so, na suro wo Nyankopɔn.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na w’akoa ne w’afenaa a wobɛnya no, amanaman a wɔgugu mo ho no, wɔn mu na tɔ akoa ne afenaa.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na ahɔhoɔ a wɔatu abɛtena mo nkyɛn no mma no nso, montɔ wɔn mu bi ne wɔn abusuafoɔ a wɔne mo teɛ a wɔawo wɔn mo asase soɔ no bi, na wɔnyɛ mo agyapadeɛ,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> na moagya wɔn ama mo mma wɔ mo akyi ayɛ wɔn awunnyadeɛ ne adeɛ a wɔdi so daa, na wɔnsom mo nkoasom; na mo nuanom Israelfoɔ deɛ, obiara mmfa nyadie nnhyɛ ne nua so.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Na sɛ wo nkyɛn hɔhoɔ anaa otubrafoɔ bi nsam wɔ biribi, na ɛhia wo nua a ɔne no wɔ hɔ, na wɔtɔn no ma ɔhɔhoɔ a watu abɛtena wo nkyɛn anaa ɔhɔhoɔ no abusua mu nipa bi a,",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> ɛnneɛ, ne tɔn akyiri no, wɔmma ne gyeɛ ho kwan; ne nuanom mu baako nnye no,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> anaasɛ n’agya nua anaa n’agya nua ba nnye no, anaasɛ n’abusua mu bogya bi nnye no, anaasɛ ne nsam wɔ biribi a, ɔnnye ne ho.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Na ɔne deɛ ɔtɔɔ no no mmu nkonta mfiri afe a wɔtɔn no maa no no so nkɔsi ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no so, na ne tiriadeɛ nyɛ sɛdeɛ mfeɛ no dodoɔ teɛ, ɔne no asetena nyɛ sɛ ɔpaani nna.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Sɛ mfeɛ no da so dɔɔso a, ne tiri sika no mu gyeɛ adeɛ a ɔbɛdane ama no no nnɔɔso saa ara;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> na sɛ aka mfeɛ kakraa bi na aduru ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no so a, ɔmmu mma no: Ne mfeɛ no ano pɛ na ɔnnane ne gyeɛ adeɛ mma no:",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Ɔne no asetena nyɛ sɛ ɔpaani deɛ afe afe: Ɔmmfa nyadie nnhyɛ no so wɔ w’anim.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Na sɛ wɔamfa yeinom so annye no a, ɛnneɛ, ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no mu, ɔmfa ne ho nkɔdi, ɔno ne ne mma nyinaa.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Na me na Israelfoɔ yɛ me nkoa. Me nkoa a meyii wɔn firii Misraim asase soɔ ne wɔn: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Monnyɛ anyamehuhuo mmfa, na mommfa ahoni anaa ɔbosom dum bi nnsi hɔ mmfa, na mommfa ɔboɔ a wɔadi ho adwini nnsi mo asase so nnkoto nnsɔre wɔ ho, ɛfiri sɛ mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Monni me home nna, na monsuro me kronkronbea: Mene AWURADE.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sɛ mofa m’ahyɛdeɛ so na mohwɛ me mmara nsɛm na moyɛ a,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ɛnneɛ mɛma osuo atɔ ama mo ne berɛ mu, na asase no ama ne nnɔbaeɛ, na mfuo mu nnua aso aba;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na aduane poreɛ bɛkɔ so akɔduru bobe aba teteɛ mu, na bobe aba teteɛ no akɔ so akɔduru duaberɛ, na mobɛdi mo aduane amee, na moatena mo asase so dwoodwoo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na mɛma ɔmannwoeɛ aba asase no so, na moada na obiara anyi mo hu; na mɛsɛe mmoa bɔne afiri asase no so, na nkrantɛ remfa mo asase so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mobɛka mo atamfoɔ agu, na wɔatotɔ mo anim wɔ nkrantɛ ano;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na mo mu baanum bɛka nnipa ɔha agu, na mo mu ɔha bɛka mpemdu agu, na mo atamfoɔ atotɔ mo anim wɔ nkrantɛ ano.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mɛdane m’anim mama mo, na mɛma moawo na moadɔ, na mɛma me ne mo apam no agyina.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na mobɛdi akoradeɛ dada a akyɛre, na mobɛyi adada no agu, afoforɔ no nti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na mede me tenabea bɛsi mo mu, na mo ho renyɛ me kra nwunu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mɛnante mo mu, na mayɛ mo Nyankopɔn, na mo nso moayɛ me ɔman:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn a meyii mo firii Misraim asase so sɛ monnyɛ nkoa bio, na mebubuu mo kɔnnua na memaa monantee kyirebenn no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ moantie me na moanni me mmara nsɛm yi nyinaa so,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na sɛ mopa m’ahyɛdeɛ, na m’atemmuo yɛ mo kra nwunu, na moanni me mmara nsɛm nyinaa so na mobu m’apam so a,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> me nso deɛ mɛyɛ mo nie: Mɛma akomatudeɛ abɛto mo, nsamanwa ne ɔfoɛ a ɛbɛma mo ani ayɛ siamoo na mo kra atotɔ piti, na mobɛdua mo aduadeɛ kwa, na mo atamfoɔ abɛdi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mɛma m’ani asa mo, na moadi mo atamfoɔ anim nkoguo na wɔn a wɔkyiri mo ahyɛ mo so, na obi mpamo mo po a, moadwane.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na sɛ yeinom mu moantie me ara a, ɛnneɛ mo bɔne nti mɛtwe mo aso mprɛnson aka ho,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na mabubu mo ahoɔden ahokyerɛ no. Na mɛyɛ mo soro sɛ dadeɛ, na mo asase ayɛ sɛ kɔbere,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na mo tumi asa kwa, na mo asase remma ne nnɔbaeɛ, na asase no so nnua renso aba.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na sɛ mone me di asie ara na mompɛ sɛ motie me a, mɛkɔ so mabɔ mo mprɛnson sɛdeɛ mo bɔne teɛ no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na mɛsoma wiram mmoa aba mo mu na wɔagye mo nsam mma, na wɔadi mo afieboa, na wɔama moasua, na mo akwan ayɛ akwan fo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na sɛ moamma mamfa yeinom ammɔ mo kɔkɔ na mone me di asie ara a,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ɛnneɛ me nso mene mo bɛdi asie, na me nso mo bɔne nti mabɔ mo mprɛnson.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mede aweretɔ nkrantɛ a ɛbɛtɔ m’apam no so were bɛba mo so, na moaboaboa mo ano akɔ mo nkuro mu, na mɛma yaredɔm aba mo mu, na wɔde mo ahyɛ ɔtamfoɔ nsa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mɛbubu mo aduane dua, na mmaa du ato mo paanoo fononoo baako mu, na wɔakari mo paanoo ama mo, na mobɛdi na moremmee.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na sɛ yei mu nso moantie me na mone me di asie ara a,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ɛnneɛ mede abufuhyeɛ ne mo bɛdi asie, na me nso mo bɔne no nti matwe mo aso mprɛnson.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na mobɛdi mo mmammarima nam, na mo mmabaa nam nso moadi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na mɛsɛe mo sorɔnsorɔmmea, na matwitwa mo aduhwam afɔrebukyia no agu, na matoto mo afunu agu mo abosonhunu afunu no so, na mo ho ayɛ me kra nwunu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na mɛgu mo nkuro mayɛ no amamfo na masɛe mo kronkronbea, na merennye mo aduhwam no hwa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na me ara mɛsɛe asase no ama mo atamfoɔ a wɔbɛtena soɔ no ani so ayɛ wɔn yaa;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> na mo deɛ, mɛbɔ mo ahwete wiase amanaman mu, na matwe nkrantɛ madi mo akyi, na mo asase bɛda hɔ tuu, na mo nkuro ayɛ akurofo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ɛno na asase no bɛnya ne homeberɛ mu ahotɔ, nna a ɛso bɛda hɔ tuu no nyinaa, na mo deɛ, mo atamfoɔ asase so na mobɛtena; ɛno na asase no bɛhome na anya ne home nna no mu ahotɔ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Nna a ɛso bɛda hɔ tuu no nyinaa na ɛbɛhome, sɛ nna dodoɔ a anhome, mo home mmerɛ mu, berɛ a na mote soɔ no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na mo mu wɔn a wɔbɛka no, mɛma ehu aba wɔn akoma mu wɔ wɔn atamfoɔ nsase no so, na ahahan a ɛteɛ huuyɛ aka wɔn agu na wɔadwane sɛdeɛ obi dwane firi nkrantɛ ano na wɔatotɔ, berɛ a obi mpamo wɔn;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> na wɔakyere abom ahwe ase sɛdeɛ wɔredwane nkrantɛ anim, berɛ a obi mpamo wɔn. Na morennya mo atamfoɔ anim agyinayɛ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na mobɛwuwu wɔ wiase amanaman mu, na mo atamfoɔ asase amene mo.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na mo mu wɔn a wɔbɛka no ho bɛhiahia wɔn wɔ wɔn amumuyɛ mu, mo atamfoɔ asase so, na wɔn agyanom amumuyɛ nso nti wɔn ho bɛhiahia wɔn sɛ wɔn agyanom no ara.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ɛno na wɔbɛka wɔn amumuyɛ ne wɔn agyanom amumuyɛ no; — sɛ, nkontompo a wɔtwaa me ne asie a wɔne me diiɛ nti,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> me nso mene wɔn dii asie, na mede wɔn kɔɔ wɔn atamfoɔ asase so; — na sɛ afei wɔn akoma momonoto no bɛbrɛ ase na wɔapene wɔn amumuyɛ ho asotwe no so a,",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> ɛnneɛ mɛkae mene Yakob apam no; ɛne mene Isak apam no nso; na mene Abraham apam no nso mɛkae, na mɛkae asase no.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na asase no deɛ, wɔbɛgya na anya ne homeberɛ no mu ahotɔ, sɛ wɔnni soɔ nti ada hɔ tuu; na wɔn deɛ, ɛsiane sɛ wɔpoo m’atemmudeɛ na m’ahyɛdeɛ yɛɛ wɔn kra nwunu nti, wɔbɛnya wɔn amumuyɛ ho asotwe, ɛfiri sɛ wɔpaa m’atemmudeɛ na m’ahyɛdeɛ yɛɛ wɔn kra nwunu.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Nanso yeinom nyinaa akyiri no, sɛ wɔwɔ wɔn atamfoɔ asase so mpo a, merempa wɔn, na wɔn ho renyɛ me nwunu na masɛe wɔn korakora, na mabu me ne wɔn ntam apam no so: Na mene AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na wɔn nti mɛkae apam a mene wɔn agyanom a meyii wɔn firii Misraim asase so wiase amanaman nyinaa anim pamm sɛ mɛyɛ wɔn Nyankopɔn no ama wɔn: Mene AWURADE.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Yeinom ne ahyɛdeɛ ne atemmudeɛ ne mmara a AWURADE de nam Mose so too ɔno ne Israelfoɔ ntam, Sinai bepɔ soɔ no."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE kasa kyerɛɛ Mose sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israelfoɔ na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ obi hyɛ bɔ titire bi a, nnipa deɛ, wɔnyɛ AWURADE deɛ, sɛdeɛ wobɛbɔ wɔn boɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɛboɔ a bɔ nie: Ɔbarima a wadi mfirinhyia aduonu de kɔsi mfeɛ aduosia, ɛboɔ a bɔ nyɛ nnwetɛbena aduonum sɛdeɛ kronkronbea dwetɛbena teɛ no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na sɛ ɔyɛ ɔbaa a, wo boɔ nnyina nnwetɛbena aduasa;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na sɛ wadi mfeɛ nnum de kɔsi mfeɛ aduonu na sɛ ɔyɛ ɔbarima a, wo boɔ nyɛ nnwetɛbena aduonu, na sɛ ɔyɛ ɔbaa a, nnwetɛbena du.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ wadi bosome baako de kɔsi mfeɛ nnum a, wo boɔ a wode bɛbɔ ɔbarima nyɛ nnwetɛbena nnum, na ɔbaa deɛ, wo boɔ nyɛ nnwetɛbena mmiɛnsa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ wadi mfeɛ aduosia anaasɛ deɛ ɛboro saa na ɔyɛ ɔbarima a, wo boɔ nyɛ nnwetɛbena dunum, na sɛ ɔyɛ ɔbaa a, nnwetɛbena du.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na sɛ ohia aka no a enti ɔntumi mma wo boɔ a wobɔeɛ no a, wɔmfa no mmɛgyina ɔsɔfoɔ no anim, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmɔ no boɔ; sɛdeɛ deɛ wahyɛ bɔ no nsa bɛso soɔ, na ɔsɔfoɔ no mmɔ no boɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ ɛyɛ afieboa a wɔde bi brɛ AWURADE sɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ no bi a, adeɛ a wɔde bi brɛ AWURADE nyinaa yɛ kronkron.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wɔnnsakyera, na wɔmmfa papa nnsesa bɔne anaasɛ bɔne nnsesa papa; na sɛ sesa na wɔde aboa sesa aboa a, ɛnneɛ ɛno ne deɛ wɔde sesaeɛ no nyinaa nyɛ kronkron.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ ɛyɛ aboa biara a ne ho nteɛ a wɔmfa no mmrɛ AWURADE sɛ ayɛyɛdeɛ a, wɔmmfa aboa no mmɛgyina ɔsɔfoɔ anim,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na sɛ ɛyɛ oo, ɛnyɛ oo, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmɔ ne boɔ; sɛdeɛ wo, sɔfoɔ no, bɛbɔ no, saa ara na ɛnnyina.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ ɔpɛ sɛ ɔgyeɛ a, ɛnneɛ ɔmfa wo boɔ no abupɛn nnum mu baako nka ho.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na sɛ obi yɛ ne fie kronkron sɛ ɛnyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE a, sɛ ɛyɛ oo, ɛnyɛ oo, ɔsɔfoɔ no mmɔ ne boɔ; sɛdeɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no bɛbɔ no, saa ara na ɛnnyina.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛ deɛ ɔyɛɛ no kronkron no bɛgye ne fie no a, ɔmfa wo boɔ no dwetɛ abupɛn nnum mu baako nto so, na ɛnyɛ ne deɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na sɛ obi yɛ n’asase a ɔdi soɔ kronkron ma AWURADE a, wo boɔ bɔ nyɛ sɛdeɛ n’aduadeɛ teɛ; bɔ atokoɔ a wɔdua homer baako boɔ nnwetɛbena aduonum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sɛ ɔfiri ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe so yɛ n’asase no kronkron a, ɛnnyina wo boɔ no so;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na sɛ ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no akyi na ɔyɛ n’asase no kronkron a, ɛnneɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu n’akonta mma no sɛdeɛ mfeɛ a aka na ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe aduro no teɛ no, na wɔnte wo boɔ no so.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ gyeɛ na deɛ ɔyɛɛ asase no kronkron no bɛgyeɛ a, ɔmfa wo boɔ no dwetɛ abupɛn nnum mu baako nto so, na ɛntena ne nsam;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na sɛ wannye asase no na wɔtɔn ma obi a, wɔnnnye bio,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na sɛ asase no nni wura ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no mu a, ɛnyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE, sɛ asase a wɔahyira so de ama; ɛnyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ no agyapadeɛ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na sɛ ɔyɛ asase a ɔtɔeɛ a ɛnyɛ n’asase a ɔdi soɔ bi kronkron ma AWURADE a,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ɔsɔfoɔ no mmu akonta mma no nkyerɛ no wo boɔ no mu deɛ ɛbɛka akɔsi ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no soɔ, na ɔmma wo boɔ a wobɔeɛ no da no ara; ɛyɛ kronkron ma AWURADE.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ahosɛpɛ afahyɛ afe no so, asase no nsane nkɔyɛ deɛ ɔtɔɔ no ne nkyɛn a ɛyɛ n’asase a ɔdi soɔ no dea.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wo boɔ a wobɛbɔ nyinaa nyɛ sɛdeɛ kronkronbea dwetɛbena no teɛ; gera aduonu yɛ dwetɛbena baako.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na afieboa mu mmakan a wɔawo ama AWURADE no nko deɛ, obi nnyɛ wɔn kronkron; nantwie oo, odwan oo, ɛyɛ AWURADE dea.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na sɛ ɛyɛ afieboa a wɔn ho nteɛ no bi a, ɛnneɛ ɔnnye no wo boɔ a wobɛbɔ no so, na ɔmfa abupɛn nnum mu baako nto so; na sɛ wɔannye no a, ɛnneɛ wɔntɔn no sɛdeɛ wobɛbɔ ne boɔ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nso ahyiradeɛ biara a obi bɛhyira so ama AWURADE, adeɛ a ɔwɔ nyinaa mu no, onipa oo, aboa oo, n’asase a ɔdi so oo, ɛno deɛ wɔnntɔn, na wɔnnnye nso; ahyiradeɛ biara yɛ akronkronneɛ mu ade kronkron ma AWURADE.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Obiara a wɔabu no kumfɔ no, wɔnnnye; kum na wɔnku no.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na asase no so aduane ntotosoɔ du du a ɛfiri asase so aduadeɛ ne nnua so aba mu no nyinaa yɛ AWURADE dea; ɛyɛ kronkron ma AWURADE.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na sɛ obi pɛ sɛ ɔgye ne ntotosoɔ du du no bi a, ɔmfa abupɛn nnum mu baako nto so.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na anantwie ne nnwan mu ntotosoɔ du du nyinaa, adeɛ a ɛfa odwanhwɛfoɔ poma ase nyinaa mu deɛ ɛtɔ so du du no, ɛnyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Wɔmmpa papa ne bɔne mu, na wɔnnsesa ebi nso; na sɛ obi bɛsesa ebi a, ɛnneɛ ɛno ne deɛ wɔde resesa no nyinaa nyɛ kronkron mma AWURADE; wɔnnnye.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Yeinom ne mmara nsɛm a AWURADE de hyɛɛ Mose, Sinai bepɔ soɔ, maa no de kɔmaa Israel mma no."
		}
	}
};
